Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意了 风暴依旧在向西移动\N{\fs36}...and I'll tell you what, the storm system's still moving west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么呢 Caroline\N{\fs36}What are you looking at, Caroline?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看风 妈妈\N{\fs36}The wind, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说飓风要来了\N{\fs36}They say the hurricane is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉我在船上\N{\fs36}I'm on a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随波漂流着\N{\fs36}I'm drifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我为你做点什么吗 妈妈\N{\fs36}Can I do anything for you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你舒服点\N{\fs36}Make anything easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 宝贝\N{\fs36}Oh, sugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么可做的了\N{\fs36}There's nothing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此 就这样了\N{\fs36}Is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想睁眼都变得更难了\N{\fs36}Finding it harder to keep my eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉嘴里都是棉絮\N{\fs36}My mouth's full of cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 好了 Daisy女士\N{\fs36}There, there, Miss Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会把自己抓烂的\N{\fs36}You gonna scratch yourself to ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你还想加大药量吗\N{\fs36}Do you want any more medication, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说你想要多少就用多少\N{\fs36}Doctor said you could have as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大家都不用遭罪\N{\fs36}No need for anybody to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个朋友告诉我 她都没有机会\N{\fs36}A friend told me that she never had the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她妈妈告别\N{\fs36}to say goodbye to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想  - 没事的\N{\fs36}- I wanted to... - it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诉你 我会很想你的\N{\fs36}I wanted to tell you how much I'm gonna miss you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Caroline\N{\fs36}Oh, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕吗\N{\fs36}Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好奇\N{\fs36}I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会怎么样呢\N{\fs36}What comes next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在1918年建造了火车站\N{\fs36}They built the train station in 1918.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车站开始运营的那天 我爸爸也去了\N{\fs36}My father was there the day it opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 那天请了\N{\fs36}He said they had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铜管乐队去表演\N{\fs36}a tuba band playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:03:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请了全南方最优秀的钟表匠\N{\fs36}They had the finest clockmaker in all of the South
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打造了那座绝美的钟\N{\fs36}to build that glorious clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钟表匠叫\N{\fs36}His name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gateau先生\N{\fs36}Mr. Gateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.19,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Gateau在法语中意为蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生\N{\fs36}Mr. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他娶了伊文格琳县的一位克里奥尔人\N{\fs36}He was married to a Creole of Evangeline Parish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.76,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Creole 带有法国血统的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且有了个儿子\N{\fs36}and they had a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gateau先生天生盲障\N{\fs36}Mr. Gateau was, from birth, absolutely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的儿子到了年龄 就去参军了\N{\fs36}When their son was old enough, he joined the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们祈祷上帝能保佑儿子免受灾难\N{\fs36}And they prayed God would keep him out of harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多月以来 他什么都没做 只专注打造那个钟\N{\fs36}For months, he did nothing but work on that clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天\N{\fs36}One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们收到了一封信\N{\fs36}a letter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gateau先生结束当晚的工作后\N{\fs36}And Mr. Gateau, done for the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自上楼睡觉了\N{\fs36}went up, alone, to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的儿子被送了回来\N{\fs36}And their son came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把他埋在家族墓地里\N{\fs36}They buried him in the family plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他们去世 将和儿子一起埋在这里\N{\fs36}where he would be with them when their time came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生继续打造那座钟\N{\fs36}Mr. Cake worked on his clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力以赴 终于完成\N{\fs36}laboring to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个值得纪念的早晨\N{\fs36}It was a morning to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸说那里人山人海\N{\fs36}Papa said there were people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连Teddy Roosevelt都去了\N{\fs36}Even Teddy Roosevelt came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.00,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,美国第26任总统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钟是倒着走的\N{\fs36}It's running backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这么设计的\N{\fs36}I made it that way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 也许那些我们在战争中失去的孩子们\N{\fs36}so that perhaps the boys that we lost in the war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死而复生 回到家乡\N{\fs36}might stand and come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家耕种\N{\fs36}Home to farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作\N{\fs36}work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生儿育女\N{\fs36}have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着充实 长久的生活\N{\fs36}To live long, full lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我的儿子会回来\N{\fs36}Perhaps my own son might come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有冒犯 还请原谅\N{\fs36}I'm sorry if I've offended anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们喜欢我的钟\N{\fs36}I hope you enjoy my clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生从此杳无音信\N{\fs36}Mr. Cake was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说他因心碎而死\N{\fs36}Some say he died of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说他下海远航了\N{\fs36}Some say he went to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fs36}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意我打个电话吗 我让别人在照看我儿子\N{\fs36}Do you mind if I make a call? Somebody's watching my little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs36}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我没有让你失望\N{\fs36}I hope I haven't disappointed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会让我失望呢\N{\fs36}You couldn't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我自己没什么本事\N{\fs36}Well, I know I don't have much to show for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把我深色的手提箱找出来\N{\fs36}Find my dark suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有一本日记\N{\fs36}There's a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本吗\N{\fs36}This?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能读给我听吗\N{\fs36}Could you read it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你想做的事吗\N{\fs36}Is this what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想读它有百余遍了\N{\fs36}I tried to read it a hundred different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 这也不是\N{\fs36}Mom, it's not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 我只是想听你的声音\N{\fs36}It's just the sound of your voice, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间是1985年4月4日\N{\fs36}It's dated April 4th, 1985.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点写的是新奥尔良\N{\fs36}And it says New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这是我的遗嘱\N{\fs36}"This is my last will and testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有留下什么 没有财产 没有钱 什么都没有\N{\fs36}I don't have much to leave, few possessions, no money, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将像来到这个世界的时候一样\N{\fs36}I will go out of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孑然一身地离开这个世界\N{\fs36}the same way I came in, alone and with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所拥有的 就是我的故事\N{\fs36}All I have is my story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我还记得 我要把它写下来\N{\fs36}And I'm writing it now while I still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Benjamin Benjamin Button"\N{\fs36}My name is Benjamin. Benjamin Button."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出身在一个不同寻常的时间里\N{\fs36}And I was born under unusual circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一战结束的那天\N{\fs36}The First World War had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人告诉我 那是一个适合出生的好夜晚\N{\fs36}and I've been told it was an especially good night to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争终于结束了\N{\fs36}Thank God it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了\N{\fs36}We won the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大战结束了\N{\fs36}The Great War is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛\N{\fs36}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thomas\N{\fs36}Thomas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕她快不行了\N{\fs36}I'm afraid she's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs36}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 你们所有人都离她远点儿\N{\fs36}That's enough. All of you, get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽可能快地赶来了 街上都是人\N{\fs36}I came as quickly as I could. The streets are filled with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thomas\N{\fs36}Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我保证 他会有容身之所\N{\fs36}Promise me he has a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为我失去了生命\N{\fs36}She gave her life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 我一直心怀感激\N{\fs36}And for that, I am forever grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Button先生\N{\fs36}Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thomas\N{\fs36}Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thomas\N{\fs36}Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thomas 你要去哪里\N{\fs36}Thomas? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你在那儿干什么\N{\fs36}Hey! What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怀里抱的是什么\N{\fs36}What do you have there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 来 Queenie  - 别这样 Weathers先生\N{\fs36}- Come on, Queenie. - Now, Mr. Weathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嘛 你也知道\N{\fs36}Come on, now, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里还有一堆活要干呢\N{\fs36}I ain't got nothing but work to do around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没事 就耽误一点时间  - 别这么傻了\N{\fs36}- Come on. Just take some time. - Stop all this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气真好\N{\fs36}The air is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚格外迷人 Queenie小姐\N{\fs36}You look very handsome tonight, Miss Queenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我见过的最美的人\N{\fs36}Handsome as I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棕色很衬你的眼睛\N{\fs36}The brown matches your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 别说了\N{\fs36}Oh, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你 你也不邋遢啊\N{\fs36}Let's see here. You ain't no slouch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hambert回来了\N{\fs36}Hambert's back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的腿没了 但好歹回来了\N{\fs36}He came home legless, but he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你曾经喜欢他\N{\fs36}I know you were sweet on him one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢得过火了\N{\fs36}Sweeter than I should've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Simone女士把自己尿湿了\N{\fs36}Miss Simone messed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的神啊\N{\fs36}Oh, sweet Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她再这样就要给她穿尿布了\N{\fs36}She got to stop doing that or it's diapers for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我马上去 Jameson女士  - 别走嘛 Queenie 过来\N{\fs36}- I'll be right there, Miss Jameson! - Now, Queenie, now come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie马上就去\N{\fs36}Okay, Queenie'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面多好啊\N{\fs36}It's awful nice out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面待一会儿吧 你好好轻松一下\N{\fs36}Come on out back for a moment. Take your mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个坏人\N{\fs36}You're so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天 怎么回事  - 这是什么啊\N{\fs36}- What in God's name? - What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 上帝做了什么啊\N{\fs36}Oh, the Lord done something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我刚没有踩伤他\N{\fs36}Hope I didn't hurt it none stepping on it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好让警察来处理\N{\fs36}We best leave that for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的小生命\N{\fs36}Poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找警察\N{\fs36}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定没有人愿意收留他 来 宝贝\N{\fs36}It's for sure nobody wanted to keep it. Come on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie 你在哪儿 Queenie\N{\fs36}Queenie? Where are you, Queenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先憋着 你去看一下\N{\fs36}Hold your water! You go deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 快去 我马上来\N{\fs36}Okay. No, go, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie 亲爱的 她又把自己尿湿了\N{\fs36}Queenie, Apple, she went and messed herself all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jane Childress 给她洗个澡\N{\fs36}Jane Childress, start her a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管好你自己的事 Duprey太太\N{\fs36}And mind your own business, Mrs. Duprey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快要尿裤子了\N{\fs36}You'll be messing yourself soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人偷了我的项链\N{\fs36}Somebody stole my necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 Hollister太太 我马上来 好吗\N{\fs36}Okay. All right, Mrs. Hollister, I'll be right with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回楼上去 听见了吗\N{\fs36}Go on back upstairs, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丑得就像一个破罐子\N{\fs36}You are as ugly as an old pot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你仍是上帝的孩子\N{\fs36}but you're still a child of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie 亲爱的 你不来她不肯洗澡\N{\fs36}Queenie, Apple, she won't take a bath without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧\N{\fs36}Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就来了\N{\fs36}I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 你就在这里等我 好吗\N{\fs36}Okay. You just wait right here for me now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这珍珠项链是我姐姐送的 我哪儿都找不到\N{\fs36}My sister gave me those pearls. I can't find them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人一直在偷我的珠宝\N{\fs36}Somebody's been stealing my jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们就在这儿呢 Hollister太太 你看\N{\fs36}They're right here, Mrs. Hollister. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你那白皙的脖子上呢\N{\fs36}Right around your pretty white neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要再说话了\N{\fs36}Now, come on. Hush all that noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rose医生还在吗  - 我不知道\N{\fs36}- Is Dr. Rose still here? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心脏很健康\N{\fs36}Your heart is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要避免任何过度刺激\N{\fs36}You just want to avoid any undue stimulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信诸位女士会帮我的 对吗\N{\fs36}I trust you ladies will help me out with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事相求 你能下楼来一下吗\N{\fs36}I have something. Could you come downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过这种东西 白内障导致他几乎失明\N{\fs36}Never seen anything like it. Nearly blind from cataracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他能否听见 他的骨骼表明他患有严重关节炎\N{\fs36}I'm not sure if he can hear. His bones indicate severe arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的皮肤失去了弹性\N{\fs36}His skin has lost all elasticity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四肢也已经硬化\N{\fs36}and his hands and feet are ossified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他表现出来的衰竭\N{\fs36}He shows all the deterioration,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和虚弱 一点都不像新生儿\N{\fs36}the infirmities, not of a newborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而像是一个行将就木的耄耋老人\N{\fs36}but of a man well in his 80s on his way to the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要死了吗\N{\fs36}He's dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他的生活开始前 他的身体就要辜负他了\N{\fs36}His body is failing him before his life's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是哪来的\N{\fs36}Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐的孩子 从拉斐特来的\N{\fs36}My sister's child. From Lafayette.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她遭遇了不幸\N{\fs36}She had an unfortunate adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可怜的孩子更惨 生来是白人\N{\fs36}The poor child, he got the worst of it. Come out white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有地方专门收留这些弃婴的 Queenie\N{\fs36}There are places for unwanted babies like these, Queenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可养不起他了\N{\fs36}No room for another mouth to feed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管Nolan基金会是出于好意\N{\fs36}The Nolan Foundation, despite their good intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们觉得这地方是个大麻烦\N{\fs36}thinks this place is a large nuisance as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一个婴儿  - 你说他活不长了\N{\fs36}- A baby... - You said he don't have long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie 有些生物注定无法生存\N{\fs36}Queenie, some creatures aren't meant to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个婴儿 是个奇迹 这是肯定的\N{\fs36}No, this baby, he is a miracle. That's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是他不是大家期盼的那种奇迹\N{\fs36}Just not the kind of miracle one hopes to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听着 听好了\N{\fs36}Y'all listen. Y'all listen up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有位客人\N{\fs36}We're gonna have us a visitor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我们住一段时间\N{\fs36}that's gonna be staying with us for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐生了个小孩 可是她不能抚养 所以\N{\fs36}My sister had a child and she couldn't see right by it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫\N{\fs36}He's known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身体不好\N{\fs36}He's not a well child,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要好好照顾他\N{\fs36}so we're gonna have to take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生了10个孩子\N{\fs36}I had 10 children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有孩子照顾不好的 让我看看他\N{\fs36}There's not a baby I can't care for. Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪 他长得真像我前夫\N{\fs36}God in Heaven. He looks just like my ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的 他过早衰老\N{\fs36}Look, he's prematurely old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rose医生说他活不了多久了\N{\fs36}Dr. Rose said he ain't got much more time on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一样\N{\fs36}Join the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在笑呢\N{\fs36}He's smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hambert让我替他问好\N{\fs36}Hambert sends his remembrances to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是疯了\N{\fs36}Are you right out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs36}I know you ain't got all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没法有自己的孩子\N{\fs36}the parts it takes to make one of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也不该收养他\N{\fs36}but this ain't yours to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也许都不是人类\N{\fs36}It may not even be humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Weathers先生 回来\N{\fs36}Mr. Weathers, come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fs36}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世事难料\N{\fs36}You never know what's coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子 我找到了归宿\N{\fs36}It seemed I had found a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事是真的吗\N{\fs36}ls any of this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的声音真好听\N{\fs36}You have such a lovely voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 这是张旧电车票\N{\fs36}Mom, it's an ancient streetcar token.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那座钟一直走着\N{\fs36}That clock just kept going,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年复一年\N{\fs36}year after year after year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道我是个孩子\N{\fs36}But I didn't know I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都是这些乱七八糟的\N{\fs36}Same old crap every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我跟这些人一样\N{\fs36}I thought I was like everyone else there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个迟暮的老人\N{\fs36}An old man in the twilight of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能让他别玩了吗\N{\fs36}Could you make him stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再敲叉子了\N{\fs36}Stop banging that fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉子是用来吃饭的 不是用来玩的\N{\fs36}It's used for eating, not for playing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 戴好你的餐巾 好吗 Benjamin先生\N{\fs36}And use your napkin, please, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie\N{\fs36}Queenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着点 小子\N{\fs36}Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是有很强的好奇心\N{\fs36}Always had a healthy curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上是什么样的 下个路口是什么样的\N{\fs36}What was up the street? Or around the next corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他\N{\fs36}Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 这样很危险 赶紧回来\N{\fs36}Benjamin! That is dangerous. Come back over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱跑 孩子\N{\fs36}Stay put, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很爱她\N{\fs36}I loved her very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的母亲\N{\fs36}She was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候 我会觉得我跟前一天有所不同\N{\fs36}Some days I feel different than the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人对自己的感受都不同 不管是哪方面\N{\fs36}Everybody feels different about themselves, one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们都要去向同一个地方\N{\fs36}But we're all going the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是选择了不同的路 就是这样\N{\fs36}Just taking different roads to get there, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走好自己的路 Benjamin\N{\fs36}You're on your own road, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我还能活多久\N{\fs36}Mama? How much longer I got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要对你的所得心怀感激就行 明白吗\N{\fs36}Just be thankful for what you're given, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经比预想的活得长了\N{\fs36}You're already here longer than you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些夜晚 我得独自睡觉\N{\fs36}Some nights, I'd have to sleep alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不介意\N{\fs36}I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会聆听房子里的声音\N{\fs36}I would listen to the house breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都已入睡\N{\fs36}All those people sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很有安全感\N{\fs36}I felt safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的生活很有规律\N{\fs36}It was a place of great routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管天气如何 每天早晨5点半\N{\fs36}Every morning at 5:30, no matter the weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退伍的美军Winslow将军都会升旗\N{\fs36}General Winslow, U. S. Army, Retired, would raise the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小有名气的前歌剧家Sybil Wagner太太\N{\fs36}Mrs. Sybil Wagner, once an opera singer of some note,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会唱Wagner的歌剧\N{\fs36}well, she sang Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.06,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Wagner 德国歌剧家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 宝贝 来\N{\fs36}All right, baby, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得给你这对老腿增添点活力\N{\fs36}We got to put some life into these old sticks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能走路的话\N{\fs36}Get you walking so you can
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能帮我分担事情了 来 明白吗\N{\fs36}help me out around here. Come on now, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管何季 晚餐总是在5点半准时开始\N{\fs36}No matter the season, supper was served promptly at 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坛浆\N{\fs36}Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖浆\N{\fs36}Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖浆\N{\fs36}Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我5岁开始学习阅读\N{\fs36}I learned to read when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷是个著名演员的服装师\N{\fs36}My grandfather was a dresser for a famous actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会把所有剧本带回家让我读\N{\fs36}He brung home every play for me to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我这苟延残喘之人的善良的看守者们\N{\fs36}"Kind keepers of my weak decaying age,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:00.77,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,出自莎士比亚<亨利六世>上篇第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让垂死的Mortimer在此歇息一下吧\N{\fs36}Let dying Mortimer here rest himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长期监禁让我的四肢痛苦不堪\N{\fs36}Even like a man new haled from the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同刚被从刑架上拖下来一般\N{\fs36}So fare my limbs with long imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这灰白的发丝和对死亡的追随\N{\fs36}And these gray locks, the pursuivants of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预示着Edmund Mortimer的死期即将来临"\N{\fs36}Argue the end of Edmund Mortimer."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是以为我什么都不懂\N{\fs36}You thought I was plain ignorant, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷是为John Wilkes Booth工作的\N{\fs36}The actor my grandfather worked for was John Wilkes Booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个人暗杀了林肯\N{\fs36}He killed Abraham Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世事难料\N{\fs36}You never know what's coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周六晚上 妈妈会带我去教堂\N{\fs36}On Saturday nights, Mama would make me go to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 阿门 阿门  - 阿门 阿门\N{\fs36}- Amen! Amen! - Amen! Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能为你做什么呢 小姐\N{\fs36}What can I do for you, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的器官天生有恙\N{\fs36}Her parts are all twisted up inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此不能生育\N{\fs36}and she can't have little children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊 如果你能看清一切 原谅这个女人的罪孽\N{\fs36}Lord, if you could see clear to forgive this woman her sins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让她能够生儿育女\N{\fs36}so she can bear the fruit of the womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走远吧 你这可恶的折磨\N{\fs36}Out, damnable affliction!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 歌颂上帝  - 歌颂上帝\N{\fs36}- Praise God! - Praise God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈利路亚\N{\fs36}Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亚  - 哈利路亚\N{\fs36}- Hallelujah! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位老人有什么病痛呢\N{\fs36}And what's this old man's irrediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔鬼缠上了他\N{\fs36}He's got the Devil on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想提早把他带入坟墓\N{\fs36}trying to ride him into the grave before his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走远吧 恶魔  - 走远\N{\fs36}- Out, Zebuchar! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走远吧 堕落天使  - 走远\N{\fs36}- Out, Beelzebub! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多大了\N{\fs36}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七岁 但我看起来老很多\N{\fs36}Seven. But I look a lot older.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑\N{\fs36}God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才七岁\N{\fs36}He's seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个乐观向上的人\N{\fs36}Now, this is a man with optimism in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没错  - 灵魂镌刻着信仰的人\N{\fs36}- All right. - Belief in his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是的\N{\fs36}'Yes! 'Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在上帝眼中都是孩子\N{\fs36}We are all children in the eyes of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是啊  - 哈里路亚\N{\fs36}- Yes! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把你从轮椅中解放出来\N{\fs36}We are gonna get you out of that chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们要让你用双脚走路  - 阿门\N{\fs36}- And we're gonna have you walk. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs36}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上帝荣耀之名\N{\fs36}In the name of God's glory...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.67,0:24:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来吧\N{\fs36}Rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs36}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.81,0:24:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 走走\N{\fs36}Come on. Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.68,0:24:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 孩子 快点\N{\fs36}Come on, son. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.23,0:24:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 加油试试 孩子  - 加油\N{\fs36}- Come on with it, son. Come on. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.06,0:24:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝会一路看着你的\N{\fs36}Now God is gonna see you the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.54,0:24:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会看到这个小老头\N{\fs36}He's gonna see this little old
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.00,0:24:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用拐杖也能走下去\N{\fs36}man walk without the use of a crutch or a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.40,0:24:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会看到你靠着信仰\N{\fs36}He's gonna see that you walk from faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈里路亚  - 和神灵的鼓舞独自走下去\N{\fs36}- Hallelujah! -...and divine inspiration alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:24:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 太好了  - 嘿 Ben\N{\fs36}- Yes. - Hey, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.66,0:24:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走吧 孩子  - 走走看\N{\fs36}- Go, son! - Now walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.08,0:25:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就这样  - 走\N{\fs36}- Yes. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.41,0:25:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰他\N{\fs36}Don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 小老头\N{\fs36}Rise up, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Lazarus一样站起来\N{\fs36}Rise up like Lazarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:12.16,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Lazarus死亡后 耶稣一口断定他将复活 四天后Lazarus果然复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 站起来\N{\fs36}I said, rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里路亚\N{\fs36}Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.02,0:25:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fs36}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.93,0:25:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs36}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说哈里路亚\N{\fs36}Say hallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈里路亚  - 哈里路亚\N{\fs36}- Hallelujah! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.44,0:25:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fs36}Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着走 没错\N{\fs36}Walk on. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 Benjamin\N{\fs36}That's right, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.52,0:25:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来 那的确是个奇迹\N{\fs36}Now when I look back on it, it was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道这样一句话\N{\fs36}But you know the saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有所得 必有所失\N{\fs36}the Lord giveth and the Lord taketh away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向主致以最崇高的敬意\N{\fs36}Glory in the highest!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.13,0:25:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs36}Sweet Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不要啊  - 不要\N{\fs36}- No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有很多人过生日\N{\fs36}There were so many birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.60,0:25:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个快乐的好伙伴 他是个快乐的好伙伴\N{\fs36}For he's a jolly good fellow For he's a jolly good fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.05,0:26:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的蜡烛用不完 因为我们都省着用\N{\fs36}So we wouldn't run out, we would spare the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie 你知道我就不喜欢过生日也不喜欢吃蛋糕\N{\fs36}Queenie, you know I don't like birthdays and I don't like cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神是这里的常客 有人来 有人去\N{\fs36}And death was a common visitor. People came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.28,0:26:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人离开时 你总能感觉到\N{\fs36}You always knew when someone left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.78,0:26:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的房子寂静无声\N{\fs36}There was a silence in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.34,0:26:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是适合成长的好地方\N{\fs36}It was a wonderful place to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.71,0:26:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身边的人\N{\fs36}I was with people who had
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.90,0:26:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都抛开了过往生活的矛盾\N{\fs36}shed all the inconsequences of earlier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.88,0:26:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只关心天气 洗澡水的温度\N{\fs36}Left wondering about the weather, the temperature of a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.08,0:26:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一天将要结束时的阳光\N{\fs36}the light at the end of a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有人来填补那些死者的房间\N{\fs36}For everyone that died, someone would come to take their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.86,0:26:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我结了五次婚\N{\fs36}I've been married five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:27:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的第五任妻子\N{\fs36}My fifth wife and I are
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.01,0:27:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被附近的食人族部落抓住了\N{\fs36}captured by a neighbor tribe of cannibals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\fs36}Oh, goodness gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跨过河流逃跑\N{\fs36}We escaped across the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.20,0:27:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子不会游泳 很不幸 她被吃了\N{\fs36}My wife, she can't swim, so, sadly, she eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.71,0:27:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs36}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.00,0:27:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第二任妻子踩到毒蛇 也死了\N{\fs36}My second wife steps on cobra and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.38,0:27:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我结婚 真的很晦气\N{\fs36}It was very bad luck to be married to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.26,0:27:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Oti先生 他是我一熟人的熟人\N{\fs36}That's Mr. Oti. He's an acquaintance of an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.38,0:27:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 第二年夏天 我和我的  - 他是俾格米人\N{\fs36}- The next summer I'm captured... - He's a Pygmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.38,0:27:21.51,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,身高不满5英尺(约1.5米)的矮小人种
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.59,0:27:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他三位妻子被抓到巴齐里部落\N{\fs36}...with three others by the Baschiele tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们用我们 跟一个陌生美国人\N{\fs36}They trade us for pigs, shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换猪 鞋子 和啤酒\N{\fs36}and beer to a very strange American man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.58,0:27:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说 你没有看起来的那么老\N{\fs36}I hear you're not so old as you're looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了所有人\N{\fs36}You just fooling everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 感染了马甲本吗\N{\fs36}What's the matter? Did you get Madjembe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.09,0:27:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马甲本是什么\N{\fs36}What's Madjembe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:27:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子\N{\fs36}Worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.26,0:28:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不是虫子\N{\fs36}I don't think I have worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我天生就这样\N{\fs36}This is just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.81,0:28:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 一起喝杯根汁汽水\N{\fs36}Come. Let's get a cold root beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.27,0:28:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你枕头下面发现了药哦\N{\fs36}I found the medication under your pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.48,0:28:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能喝的 太危险了\N{\fs36}I'm not supposed to. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.77,0:28:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说危险的 走吧 小老头\N{\fs36}Who said that? Come on, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.78,0:28:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们好\N{\fs36}Hello, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.71,0:28:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦停车\N{\fs36}Hold, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.88,0:28:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来我在费城动物园的猴馆里\N{\fs36}Then I'm in the monkey house at Philadelphia Zoological Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.09,0:28:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一天就有三千个人来看我\N{\fs36}Three thousand people show up my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.93,0:28:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fs36}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.72,0:28:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在笼子里什么感觉\N{\fs36}What's it like living in a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.73,0:28:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别臭\N{\fs36}It stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.81,0:28:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那些猴子\N{\fs36}But the monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.90,0:28:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会玩些小把戏\N{\fs36}They do some tricks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.15,0:29:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丢长矛 和Kowali摔角\N{\fs36}I throw a spear, wrestle with Kowali.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.69,0:29:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是只红毛猩猩\N{\fs36}She is orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.86,0:29:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不跟猴子们玩儿的时候\N{\fs36}When I'm not playing with the monkeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.58,0:29:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就要我张牙舞爪地\N{\fs36}they want me to run to the bars
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.49,0:29:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲到我的铁笼前\N{\fs36}in my cage, with my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.55,0:29:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来你做了什么\N{\fs36}So then what'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.71,0:29:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开了动物园 到处闯荡 多半时间都在闲逛\N{\fs36}Then I leave zoo, go here, go there. Wandered most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.01,0:29:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你一个人\N{\fs36}You were all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.18,0:29:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数时间你都是孤单的\N{\fs36}Plenty of time you'll be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些异类 都是这样\N{\fs36}When you're different like us, it's gonna be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.02,0:29:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但告诉你个秘密\N{\fs36}But I'll tell you a little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.98,0:29:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类 不管是高矮胖瘦\N{\fs36}Fat people, skinny people, tall people,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.36,0:29:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是白人 他们和我们一样孤单\N{\fs36}white people, they're just as alone as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.91,0:29:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的是 他们怕得要死\N{\fs36}But they're scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.33,0:29:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想念我长大的那条河\N{\fs36}I think about the river I grew up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.42,0:30:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能再坐在河边 一定很美好\N{\fs36}It would be nice to sit by my river again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.59,0:30:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我要去赴约了\N{\fs36}Come, I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.39,0:30:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来啦 准备好了吗 亲爱的\N{\fs36}There's my little man. You ready, sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.06,0:30:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻准备着\N{\fs36}Always ready. Always ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.18,0:30:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Filamena 这是Benjamin先生\N{\fs36}Filamena, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.31,0:30:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 见到你很高兴 先生  - 我的荣幸 女士\N{\fs36}- It's a pleasure to meet you, sir. - My pleasure, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.48,0:30:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以自己回家的 对吧\N{\fs36}You can find your own way home, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.57,0:30:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐圣查尔斯线到拿破仑站\N{\fs36}Take the St. Charles line to Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.28,0:30:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\fs36}Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.22,0:30:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 你去哪儿了 赶紧进来\N{\fs36}Where in God's name have you been? Get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.23,0:31:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快担心死了 知道吗\N{\fs36}I mean, you take my breath away, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.90,0:31:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 我太担心你了\N{\fs36}Oh, Lord, I was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我人生中最美好的一天\N{\fs36}It had been the best day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她的呼吸怎么样了  - 很微弱\N{\fs36}- How's her breathing? -It's shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.49,0:31:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说飓风几小时内就会来了\N{\fs36}They say it'll reach us in a few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把我儿子带到我姐姐那里去\N{\fs36}so I gotta get my baby and take him to my sister's.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.12,0:31:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说医院这边没什么好担心的\N{\fs36}They say there's nothing to worry about here in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.71,0:31:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要帮助 护士就在这里 你还好吗\N{\fs36}Nurses'll be right here if you need them. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.30,0:31:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没事 我读日记呢  - 一小时内我就回来\N{\fs36}- Yeah, I'm okay reading. - I shouldn't be more than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来陪了吗\N{\fs36}Was there just company?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.40,0:31:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Dorothy要走了\N{\fs36}It was just Dorothy leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.23,0:31:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续读吧 Caroline\N{\fs36}Go on, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.77,0:31:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"到了周日 家人们会来探望"\N{\fs36}"On Sundays, the families would come and visit."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.27,0:31:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是1930年的感恩节\N{\fs36}It was Thanksgiving, 1930.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.32,0:31:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇见了改变了我一生的人\N{\fs36}I met the person who changed my life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.33,0:32:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Well, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.83,0:32:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来真是太年轻了啊\N{\fs36}Might I say you are looking strikingly youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.63,0:32:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Fuller太太\N{\fs36}Good day, Mrs. Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.30,0:32:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在用一根拐杖 背也挺得笔直\N{\fs36}A single cane, back straight as an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.68,0:32:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃了什么灵丹妙药啊\N{\fs36}What elixir have you been drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢夸奖 女士  - 奶奶 看我\N{\fs36}- Thank you, ma'am. - Grandma! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.94,0:32:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得真好\N{\fs36}That was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来\N{\fs36}Come on over here, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我孙女 Daisy\N{\fs36}Now, this is my granddaughter, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.11,0:32:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是\N{\fs36}This is Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.07,0:32:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 Benjamin 我还不知道你姓什么\N{\fs36}I'm afraid, Benjamin, I don't rightly know your last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.87,0:32:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我Benjamin就行了\N{\fs36}Benjamin's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记她那双蓝眼睛\N{\fs36}I never forgot her blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.87,0:32:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 晚餐已经好了\N{\fs36}Good people, supper is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了健康和食物 爱情和友谊\N{\fs36}Health and food, for love and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.74,0:32:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了上帝恩赐的一切\N{\fs36}For everything thy goodness sends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.10,0:32:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs36}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.24,0:32:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 阿门  - 阿门\N{\fs36}- Amen! - Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.39,0:32:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗 火鸡其实不算鸟类\N{\fs36}Did you know turkeys aren't really birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.06,0:32:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢\N{\fs36}Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.22,0:33:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们属于雉科 它们不会飞\N{\fs36}They're in the pheasant family, can't hardly fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.43,0:33:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲 对吧 不会飞的鸟\N{\fs36}It's sad, don't you think? Birds that can't fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.06,0:33:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢不会飞的鸟\N{\fs36}I love birds that can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.36,0:33:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是人间美味\N{\fs36}They are so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.53,0:33:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你太坏了  - 在我们感谢主的恩赐时\N{\fs36}- That's terrible. - I have something to tell y'all
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.00,0:33:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诉你们一件事\N{\fs36}while we're giving thanks for God's blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.37,0:33:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹降临在我身上了\N{\fs36}I had a miracle happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.78,0:33:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主竟然回应了我的祈祷\N{\fs36}The Lord saw fit to answer my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 回应了什么祈祷\N{\fs36}What does she mean, answered her prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.54,0:33:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs36}Thanks. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.17,0:33:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 她有孩子了\N{\fs36}She's gonna have a baby, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.51,0:33:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈怀上我弟弟的时候就是这么说的\N{\fs36}That's what my mama said when I was gonna have a baby brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.78,0:33:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜他命不长\N{\fs36}but he didn't live long,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他的呼吸有问题\N{\fs36}'cause he didn't breathe right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.34,0:33:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"下午 他长出了健壮漂亮的后腿\N{\fs36}"In the afternoon, when he had got his beautiful hind legs
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如大神农答应的一般\N{\fs36}Just as Big God Nqong had promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.90,0:33:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时是5点\N{\fs36}You can see that it is 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.20,0:33:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大神农的钟表上就是这么显示的"\N{\fs36}Because Big God Nqong's clock says so."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.28,0:34:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害吧\N{\fs36}Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.66,0:34:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再讲一遍嘛\N{\fs36}Again, read it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.12,0:34:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 再讲一遍嘛\N{\fs36}Oh, read it again, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.54,0:34:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 但是听完之后 你必须去睡觉\N{\fs36}All right. But afterwards, you must go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.21,0:34:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fs36}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.34,0:34:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老袋鼠"\N{\fs36}"Old Man Kangaroo."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.72,0:34:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡着了吗\N{\fs36}Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.76,0:34:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊\N{\fs36}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.36,0:34:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 Daisy\N{\fs36}It's me, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.10,0:34:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 嗨\N{\fs36}Oh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs36}'Kay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.82,0:34:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去哪儿\N{\fs36}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.64,0:34:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 到这下面来\N{\fs36}Come on. Under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.09,0:34:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来点着\N{\fs36}Here, you light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.63,0:34:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能玩火柴的\N{\fs36}I'm not supposed to play with matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么胆小 快点着\N{\fs36}Don't be a chicken. Light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.19,0:35:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你告诉我一个秘密 我也告诉你一个\N{\fs36}I'll tell you a secret if you'll tell me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.24,0:35:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.78,0:35:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见我妈妈亲了另一个男人\N{\fs36}I saw my mama kissing another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的脸都红了\N{\fs36}Her face was red from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.87,0:35:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该你了\N{\fs36}Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.67,0:35:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有看上去的那么老\N{\fs36}I'm not as old as I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.04,0:35:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得\N{\fs36}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.59,0:35:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不像个老人\N{\fs36}You don't seem like an old person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.72,0:35:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 像我奶奶一样  - 是的\N{\fs36}- Like my grandma. - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.64,0:35:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生病了吗\N{\fs36}Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.81,0:35:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听我妈妈跟Tizzy窃窃私语\N{\fs36}Well, I heard Mama and Tizzy whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.06,0:35:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说我命不久矣 但可能又不是\N{\fs36}They said I was gonna die soon, but maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:35:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真奇怪\N{\fs36}You're odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.78,0:36:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我见过的其他人都不一样\N{\fs36}You're different than anybody I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.82,0:36:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可以摸一下吗  - 好\N{\fs36}- May I? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.25,0:36:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这下面干什么\N{\fs36}What are you doing under there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.75,0:36:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我出来 回床上睡觉去\N{\fs36}You come right out here and get back up to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都大半夜了\N{\fs36}It's after midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.18,0:36:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能再一起玩了\N{\fs36}You are not to be playing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.39,0:36:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 女士\N{\fs36}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.01,0:36:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧回床上 小姑娘\N{\fs36}Now you get back to bed, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太小了 大晚上的不能一个人乱跑\N{\fs36}You're too young to be wandering around in the night on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.94,0:36:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真应该为自己感到羞耻\N{\fs36}And you ought to be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.04,0:36:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个与众不同的孩子\N{\fs36}You are a different child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.88,0:36:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是老孩子\N{\fs36}A man-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.02,0:36:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 其他人\N{\fs36}And, baby, people aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.68,0:37:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会理解你的与众不同的\N{\fs36}gonna understand just how different you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.85,0:37:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟有什么病 妈妈\N{\fs36}What's wrong with me, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.97,0:37:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs36}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.90,0:37:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝也没有告诉我 孩子\N{\fs36}God hasn't said yet, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回床上吧 好吗 管好自己\N{\fs36}Now go on to bed, hear? And behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.41,0:37:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 记得祈祷 听见了吗\N{\fs36}Go on. Say your prayers, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.80,0:37:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有告诉过你 我曾被闪电击中了7次\N{\fs36}Did I ever tell you I've been struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.18,0:37:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次是我在修补屋顶\N{\fs36}Once when I was repairing a leak on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.18,0:37:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次是过马路去取信\N{\fs36}Once I was just crossing the road to get the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记她的\N{\fs36}I never forgot her...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.87,0:38:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"蓝眼睛"\N{\fs36}"...blue eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.87,0:38:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.54,0:38:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白这个Benjamin\N{\fs36}Did you get that this Benjamin
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.80,0:38:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对你一见钟情吗\N{\fs36}loved you from the first time that he saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.55,0:38:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是谁都有这样的经历\N{\fs36}Not many people experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.51,0:38:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我继续读吗\N{\fs36}Want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.27,0:38:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他划掉了一些话\N{\fs36}He crosses something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.39,0:38:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那婴儿出生之后 一切都变了\N{\fs36}When that baby came, things were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.77,0:38:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*妈咪要离开 爹地不会走*\N{\fs36}*Your mama gone away and your daddy gonna stay*
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.23,0:38:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*谁都不会抛下你*\N{\fs36}*Didn't leave nobody but the baby*
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人出生 也有人死亡\N{\fs36}Babies were born, people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人进出过那所老房子\N{\fs36}A lot of folks been through that old house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.79,0:38:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来道别的 我要走了\N{\fs36}I've come to say goodbye. I'm going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.12,0:38:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了\N{\fs36}Going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.74,0:39:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿\N{\fs36}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.54,0:39:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没想好\N{\fs36}I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.21,0:39:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我到了那里会给你寄明信片的\N{\fs36}but I'll send you a postcard when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友呢 高个子的那个女士\N{\fs36}What about your friend, the tall lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.63,0:39:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不再是朋友了\N{\fs36}We are not friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.14,0:39:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和高个子在一起就是会这样\N{\fs36}That's what happens with tall people sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.51,0:39:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 再见了\N{\fs36}Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一年 我一个人度过了大部分的时光\N{\fs36}Spent a lot of time by myself that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.71,0:39:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\fs36}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.71,0:39:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 我是今天搬进来的\N{\fs36}- Hi. - I'm moving in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.45,0:39:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎 我们一直等你呢\N{\fs36}Welcome. We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.51,0:39:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能带她去Rousseau太太以前的房间吗\N{\fs36}Can you please show her up to Mrs. Rousseau's old room?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们一般不允许狗进房子的\N{\fs36}I'm sorry, but we usually don't allow dogs in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.10,0:39:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经很老了 也瞎得差不多了\N{\fs36}Well, she's old as the hills. She's almost blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.18,0:40:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会麻烦你们很久的\N{\fs36}She won't be a bother much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.23,0:40:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 只要不碍事 待多久都行\N{\fs36}Well, all right, long as she stays from up underfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.26,0:40:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请 女士\N{\fs36}Right this way, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.32,0:40:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管我努力回忆 我也想不起她的名字\N{\fs36}As hard as I try, I can't remember her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.57,0:40:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lawson太太还是Hartford太太\N{\fs36}Mrs. Lawson, or Mrs. Hartford.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.74,0:40:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是Maple\N{\fs36}Maybe it was Maple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.62,0:40:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的是 有时候我们最记不起的人\N{\fs36}It's funny how sometimes the people we remember the least
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.04,0:40:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却给我们留下最深刻的印象\N{\fs36}make the greatest impression on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.16,0:40:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我记得她戴着钻戒\N{\fs36}I do remember she wore diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.63,0:40:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是打扮得很漂亮 像是要出门一样\N{\fs36}And she always dressed in fine clothing, as if she was going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.50,0:40:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管她从不出门 也没人来看望她\N{\fs36}Although she never did and nobody ever came to visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她教我弹钢琴\N{\fs36}She taught me to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.52,0:40:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹得好不好不重要\N{\fs36}It's not about how well you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.90,0:40:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是你对所弹曲子的感受\N{\fs36}It's how you feel about what you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.86,0:40:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试这首\N{\fs36}Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.54,0:41:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会情不自禁沉浸在曲子中\N{\fs36}You can't help putting yourself in the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.84,0:41:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变化总在发生\N{\fs36}There were many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.93,0:41:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些你能看得到 有些看不到\N{\fs36}Some you could see, some you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.14,0:41:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如毛发开始生长了\N{\fs36}Hair had started growing in all sorts of places,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.52,0:41:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的也开始生长了\N{\fs36}along with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.77,0:41:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我感觉很好\N{\fs36}I felt pretty good, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.57,0:41:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 疼\N{\fs36}Darling, the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 妈妈 我去叫护士\N{\fs36}All right, Mom, I'll get the nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.41,0:41:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看风暴中心 这是强烈飓风\N{\fs36}Look at this eye. This is a major hurricane,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.29,0:41:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动缓慢 但伴随着最大持续风速\N{\fs36}a slow hurricane, with maximum sustained winds of...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.29,0:41:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不太好吗\N{\fs36}Not doing too good?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.00,0:41:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没人知道到底是走是留\N{\fs36}Nobody seems to know whether to stay or leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.38,0:41:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就打算待在这里了\N{\fs36}I'm gonna ride it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.76,0:41:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这样会让你舒服很多\N{\fs36}There. That should make things much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.10,0:42:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有机会道别了吗\N{\fs36}Have you had a chance to say your goodbyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.39,0:42:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸等我哥哥\N{\fs36}My father waited four hours
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.74,0:42:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从伯格赶来等了四个小时\N{\fs36}for my brother to get here from Boger City.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.98,0:42:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意走的时候没有他的陪伴\N{\fs36}Couldn't go without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.48,0:42:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她看着是个好人  - 是啊\N{\fs36}- She seems like a sweet woman. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.82,0:42:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜我没有很多时间陪她\N{\fs36}I haven't had as much time with her as I would've...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.61,0:42:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 忙吗 麻烦帮我个忙  - 失陪了\N{\fs36}- You busy? I could use your help. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs36}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.05,0:42:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Queenie会让我跟Daws先生一起"\N{\fs36}"Queenie would let me go with Mr. Daws..."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去波弗蒂角看船随波逐流\N{\fs36}...to Poverty Point to watch the boats go up and down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.10,0:42:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段日子不好过\N{\fs36}These were hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.06,0:42:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有告诉过你 我曾被闪电击中了7次\N{\fs36}Did I ever tell you I was struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.69,0:42:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次是我在田里放牛\N{\fs36}Once when I was in the field, just tending to my cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.66,0:43:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的下手没来\N{\fs36}My fourth hand didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.16,0:43:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想在这儿打工赚个两块钱吗\N{\fs36}Anybody want to make $2 for a day's work 'round here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs36}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.34,0:43:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人想老实工作赚点工钱吗\N{\fs36}Nobody wants to do an honest day's work for an honest day's pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.22,0:43:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从来不付工资\N{\fs36}He never pays.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.22,0:43:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没人想要工作吗  - 我想\N{\fs36}- Nobody wants a job? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.18,0:43:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不晕船吗 老头\N{\fs36}You got your sea legs about you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.10,0:43:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该吧\N{\fs36}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.44,0:43:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就够了\N{\fs36}Well, that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.98,0:43:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧上船 上来就知道了\N{\fs36}Get your ass on board. We'll sure as hell find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.95,0:43:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没这么开心过\N{\fs36}I was as happy as I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.70,0:43:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要个人手\N{\fs36}I need a volunteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.04,0:43:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做\N{\fs36}I would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来 船长\N{\fs36}Yes, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些鸟屎清干净\N{\fs36}Scrape off all this bird shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.04,0:43:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就做 先生\N{\fs36}Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.59,0:43:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 我还拿到了\N{\fs36}And I was actually gonna be paid for something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.59,0:43:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来拿不到的报酬\N{\fs36}I would've done for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.72,0:44:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是Mike Clark船长\N{\fs36}His name was Captain Mike Clark.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.06,0:44:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他7岁起就在拖船上了\N{\fs36}He'd been on a tugboat since he was seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.02,0:44:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上来\N{\fs36}Get moving, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.69,0:44:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs36}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.23,0:44:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在还能勃起吗\N{\fs36}Can you still get it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上都会\N{\fs36}I do every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你这老屌 能挺得又高又硬\N{\fs36}The old pole, huh? The high, hard one?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.41,0:44:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的吧\N{\fs36}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.33,0:44:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上一次碰女人是什么时候\N{\fs36}When was the last time you had a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.50,0:44:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 从没碰过  - 从没有\N{\fs36}- Never. - Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.92,0:44:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得没有 先生\N{\fs36}Not that I know of, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.47,0:44:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等\N{\fs36}Wait a minute, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.05,0:44:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说 你活了这么多年\N{\fs36}You mean to say you've been on this earth however many years
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.26,0:44:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没碰过女人\N{\fs36}and you've never had a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.23,0:44:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 这是我听过的最悲哀的事情了\N{\fs36}Damn, that's the saddest thing I've ever heard in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.78,0:45:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没碰过吗\N{\fs36}Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.78,0:45:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没有\N{\fs36}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.49,0:45:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷 你一定得跟我走\N{\fs36}Well, then, by Jesus, you are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.63,0:45:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是做什么的\N{\fs36}What did your father do?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.30,0:45:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过他\N{\fs36}I never met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.47,0:45:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个幸运的王八蛋\N{\fs36}You lucky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.30,0:45:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有父亲想做的就是压制你\N{\fs36}All fathers want to do is hold you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.56,0:45:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在我父亲的船上 日夜做工\N{\fs36}Out on my father's boat, workin' the two-a-day,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.31,0:45:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个矮胖子\N{\fs36}this little, fat bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.82,0:45:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫他"拖船爱尔兰佬"\N{\fs36}"Tug Irish," They called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.65,0:45:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我终于鼓起勇气告诉他\N{\fs36}Anyway, I finally work up the nerve and tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.91,0:45:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我可不想把我剩下的时光都浪费在这破船上"\N{\fs36}"I don't want to spend the rest of my life on a goddamn tugboat."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.70,0:45:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的意思吗\N{\fs36}You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.08,0:45:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想把你剩下的时光都浪费在破船上\N{\fs36}You don't want to spend the rest of your life on a tugboat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.83,0:45:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是这样\N{\fs36}Absolutely! Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.92,0:46:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我爸对我说什么吗\N{\fs36}So you know what my father says to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.34,0:46:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说"你他妈算哪根葱"\N{\fs36}He says, "Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.89,0:46:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你他妈以为你能做什么"\N{\fs36}"What the hell do you think you can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.14,0:46:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他说\N{\fs36}So I tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.22,0:46:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"既然你问了 那我就告诉你\N{\fs36}"Well, if you're asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为艺术家"\N{\fs36}I want to be an artist."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.32,0:46:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他笑了\N{\fs36}He laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.69,0:46:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"艺术家 你命中注定要在拖船上工作 就像我一样\N{\fs36}"An artist? God meant for you to work a tugboat, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.82,0:46:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的工作"\N{\fs36}And that's exactly what you're gonna do."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.53,0:46:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是成为了一名艺术家\N{\fs36}Well, I turned myself into an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.25,0:46:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名纹身师\N{\fs36}A tattoo artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.42,0:46:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个纹身都是我自己纹的\N{\fs36}I put on every one of these myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.76,0:46:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得把我活剥了才能让艺术脱离我\N{\fs36}You have to skin me alive to take my art away from me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.39,0:46:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了之后 要给我爸寄一只胳膊\N{\fs36}When I'm dead, I'm gonna send him my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.14,0:46:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一只\N{\fs36}That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.90,0:47:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让别人对你指指点点\N{\fs36}Don't let anyone tell you different.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.86,0:47:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去做命中注定的事\N{\fs36}You gotta do what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.32,0:47:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我注定去做一名艺术家\N{\fs36}And I happen to be a goddamned artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.03,0:47:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你现在是个船长\N{\fs36}But you're a tugboat captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.91,0:47:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mike船长\N{\fs36}Captain Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.74,0:47:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为你和你的朋友准备好了\N{\fs36}We're ready for you and your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.25,0:47:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 老头 破了你的处\N{\fs36}Let's go, old timer, eh? Break your cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.46,0:47:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们好 小可爱们  - 嘿 船长\N{\fs36}- Hello, my lovelies! - Hey, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.12,0:47:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好船长  - 你好\N{\fs36}- Hi, Captain. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.42,0:47:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs36}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.63,0:47:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他搞得我心里发毛 我不要他\N{\fs36}He gives me the willies. That is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.60,0:47:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚过得好吗 老爷爷\N{\fs36}How are you tonight, grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.56,0:47:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个难忘的夜晚\N{\fs36}It was a night to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.44,0:47:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是至尊"屌"探还是什么吗 我要休息了\N{\fs36}What are you, Dick Tracy or something? I've got to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.24,0:47:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次\N{\fs36}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.78,0:47:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 应该谢谢你 今晚过得很好\N{\fs36}- Thank you. - No, thank you. You have a nice night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.20,0:47:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你明天还在吗  - 我每晚都在 除了周日\N{\fs36}- Will you be here tomorrow? - Every night but Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.45,0:48:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我明白了谋生的意义\N{\fs36}It sure made me understand the value of earning a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.79,0:48:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 亲爱的 快点回来\N{\fs36}Good night, sweetie. Come back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.71,0:48:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱能买到的东西\N{\fs36}Things money can buy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.61,0:48:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面太脏了\N{\fs36}It's nasty out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.73,0:48:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我送你一程吧\N{\fs36}Can I offer you a ride somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太善良了 先生\N{\fs36}Well, that's awfully kind of you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.00,0:48:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Thomas Thomas Button\N{\fs36}My name is Thomas, Thomas Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.17,0:48:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我叫Benjamin  - Benjamin\N{\fs36}- I'm Benjamin. - Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.50,0:48:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识你很高兴\N{\fs36}It's a pleasure to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.18,0:48:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪里喝一杯吗\N{\fs36}Would you like to stop somewhere and have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.51,0:48:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs36}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.18,0:48:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 Button先生\N{\fs36}Evening, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.02,0:49:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生要喝什么\N{\fs36}What'll it be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.69,0:49:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 跟他的一样吧  - 我俩都要萨泽拉克\N{\fs36}- I'll have whatever he's having. - Sazerac for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.86,0:49:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加威士忌 不要白兰地\N{\fs36}With whiskey, not brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.32,0:49:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喝酒 对吗\N{\fs36}You don't drink, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.91,0:49:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是我的第一次之夜  - 怎么说\N{\fs36}- It's a night for firsts. - How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.62,0:49:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也从没去过妓院\N{\fs36}I've never been to a brothel, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.04,0:49:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是段经历\N{\fs36}Well, it's an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.71,0:49:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 凡是总有第一次\N{\fs36}It certainly is. There's a time for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.18,0:49:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 说得对  - 你们的酒\N{\fs36}- True enough. - Your drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.96,0:49:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 你的手 疼吗\N{\fs36}I don't mean to be rude, but your hands. Is that painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.51,0:49:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我天生就有些疾病\N{\fs36}Well, I was born with some form of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.22,0:49:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么疾病\N{\fs36}What kind of disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.89,0:49:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生下来就是老人\N{\fs36}I was born old.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.18,0:49:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很抱歉  - 没必要的\N{\fs36}- I'm sorry. - No need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.98,0:49:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪大没有错\N{\fs36}There's nothing wrong with old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.41,0:49:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子几年前去世了\N{\fs36}My wife passed away many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.83,0:50:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 抱歉\N{\fs36}I'm so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在分娩时死了\N{\fs36}She died in childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 敬孩子  - 敬母亲\N{\fs36}- To children. - To mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.88,0:50:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么工作的 Button先生\N{\fs36}What line of work you in, Mr. Button?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.02,0:50:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽扣生意 Button纽扣公司\N{\fs36}Buttons. Button's Buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.70,0:50:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么纽扣我们都做\N{\fs36}There isn't a button that we don't make.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.60,0:50:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最大的竞争对手是B.F.Goodrich\N{\fs36}Our biggest competition is B. F. Goodrich
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.06,0:50:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他的破拉链企业\N{\fs36}and his infernal zippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.60,0:50:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还要喝点什么吗\N{\fs36}Would you gentlemen like anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.78,0:50:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临走前再喝一杯 Benjamin\N{\fs36}One for the road, Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.94,0:50:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非让我来请 Button先生\N{\fs36}Only if you let me pay for it, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.03,0:50:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是做什么工作的\N{\fs36}So, what line of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.95,0:50:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在拖船上工作\N{\fs36}I'm a tugboat man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.59,0:50:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢和你聊天\N{\fs36}I enjoyed talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.09,0:50:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢和你喝酒\N{\fs36}I enjoyed drinking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.80,0:51:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.34,0:51:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意我偶尔过来看看你吗\N{\fs36}Would you mind if, time to time, I stopped by and said hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.85,0:51:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以 晚安 Button先生\N{\fs36}Anytime. Good night, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.81,0:51:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.31,0:51:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs36}Drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.32,0:51:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了\N{\fs36}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.78,0:51:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我去见了些人 听了听音乐\N{\fs36}Nothing. I met some people and listened to some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.54,0:51:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天呐 孩子\N{\fs36}Oh, sweet Jesus, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.75,0:51:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大是件趣事 它会悄悄接近你\N{\fs36}Growing up's a funny thing. Sneaks up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.80,0:51:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是一个人\N{\fs36}One person is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.88,0:51:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就长大成了另外一个人\N{\fs36}then suddenly somebody else has taken her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.72,0:51:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不再是原来的样子了\N{\fs36}She wasn't all elbows and knees anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.51,0:51:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 快来\N{\fs36}Benjamin! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.60,0:51:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.18,0:51:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢她来这里\N{\fs36}I loved those weekends when she'd come
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.85,0:51:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪她奶奶的那些周末\N{\fs36}and spend the night with her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.74,0:52:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy Daisy\N{\fs36}Daisy. Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.41,0:52:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看个东西吗\N{\fs36}You want to see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.70,0:52:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要保密\N{\fs36}You gotta keep it a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.68,0:52:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿好衣服 我们在外面见\N{\fs36}so get dressed. I'll meet you out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.04,0:52:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fs36}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.22,0:52:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你会游泳吗  - 你会的我都会\N{\fs36}- Can you swim? - I can do anything you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.43,0:52:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 把这个穿好 我们得快点了\N{\fs36}Here, put this on. We gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.98,0:52:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还好吗\N{\fs36}Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.61,0:52:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长\N{\fs36}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.70,0:52:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mike船长\N{\fs36}Captain Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.91,0:52:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 船长 能带我们出去吗\N{\fs36}Morning, Captain. Can you take us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.79,0:52:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道今天是什么日子吗\N{\fs36}Do you know what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.21,0:52:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日\N{\fs36}Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.59,0:52:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道周日是什么意思吗\N{\fs36}Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.05,0:53:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我昨晚喝得烂醉\N{\fs36}Means I was very drunk last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.05,0:53:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天都喝得烂醉\N{\fs36}Well, you're drunk every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.76,0:53:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是个姑娘  - 好朋友\N{\fs36}- Is that a girl? - Close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.77,0:53:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带她看看河\N{\fs36}I want to show her the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.98,0:53:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能跟外人去兜风的\N{\fs36}You're not supposed to go joyriding with civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.44,0:53:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会丢了我的执照的\N{\fs36}I could lose my license.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.41,0:53:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么呢\N{\fs36}What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.07,0:54:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠岸修一下帆布\N{\fs36}Pulled in for repair a wounded duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.61,0:54:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她都在飞了 哈\N{\fs36}She's flying now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.28,0:54:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 水手\N{\fs36}Ahoy, sailor!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.50,0:54:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我们能跟他们一起远行\N{\fs36}I wish we could go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.74,0:54:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么了 妈妈\N{\fs36}Did you say something, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.85,0:54:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气越来越不好了\N{\fs36}It's getting really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.85,0:54:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听见我声音吗 妈妈\N{\fs36}Can you hear me, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.27,0:54:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没多少时间了\N{\fs36}Time just seeped out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.70,0:54:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"世事变化飞快"\N{\fs36}"Things were changing quickly."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.62,0:54:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么回事 但你好像头发更多了\N{\fs36}I don't know how it's possible, but you seem to have more hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.25,0:54:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你我没有越来越老\N{\fs36}What if I told you that I wasn't getting older,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.40,0:55:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是比别人越来越年轻了呢\N{\fs36}but I was getting younger than everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.71,0:55:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我为你感到抱歉\N{\fs36}Well, I'd feel sorry for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.72,0:55:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你会看着你爱的人在你之前死去\N{\fs36}to have to see everybody you love die before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.68,0:55:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是份可怕的责任\N{\fs36}It's an awful responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.68,0:55:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有从那个角度思考过人生和死亡\N{\fs36}I'd never thought about life or death that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.89,0:55:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 我们注定要失去我们爱的人\N{\fs36}Benjamin, we're meant to lose the people we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎么能知道他们对我们有多重要呢\N{\fs36}How else would we know how important they are to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.90,0:55:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋季的一天 一个熟客来敲开了我们的门\N{\fs36}And one fall day, a familiar visitor came knocking on our door.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.08,0:55:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我一起去药店吗\N{\fs36}You want to go with me to the drugstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.05,0:55:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她教我怎么弹钢琴\N{\fs36}She taught me how to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.51,0:55:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 阿门  - 阿门\N{\fs36}- Amen. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.89,0:55:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她教我思念是什么感觉\N{\fs36}And she taught me what it meant to miss somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.60,0:55:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fs36}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.10,0:56:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了妓院\N{\fs36}I had gone to a brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.30,0:56:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝了人生第一杯酒\N{\fs36}I'd had my first drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.52,0:56:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一个朋友说了永别然后埋葬了另一个朋友\N{\fs36}Said goodbye to one friend and buried another.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.74,0:56:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1936年\N{\fs36}In 1936, when I was coming
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.74,0:56:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快18岁的时候\N{\fs36}to the end of the 17th year of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.49,0:56:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收起行囊 道了再见\N{\fs36}I packed my bag, said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.45,0:56:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 再见 Benjamin  - 再见\N{\fs36}- Bye, Benjamin. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.87,0:56:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活如果还是这样\N{\fs36}I knew, life being what it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.34,0:56:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能再也见不到他们了\N{\fs36}I'd probably never see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.55,0:56:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 Benjamin先生\N{\fs36}Bye, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.30,0:56:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 孩子 祝你好运  - 谢谢\N{\fs36}- Good luck to you, son. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.52,0:56:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我爱你 妈妈  - 我也爱你 孩子\N{\fs36}- I love you, Mama. - I love you, too, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.39,0:56:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得每晚都要祷告 知道吗\N{\fs36}I want you to say your prayers every night, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.48,0:56:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全\N{\fs36}Be safe, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.96,0:57:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.42,0:57:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪儿  - 海上\N{\fs36}- Where you going? - To sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.46,0:57:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你寄明信片的\N{\fs36}I'll send you a postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.34,0:57:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在哪里\N{\fs36}From everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.39,0:57:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在哪里 都要给我寄明信片\N{\fs36}Write me a postcard from everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.53,0:57:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗\N{\fs36}Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.78,0:57:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会从他去过的每个地方寄明信片给我\N{\fs36}He sent me a postcard from everywhere he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.46,0:57:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个他工作过的地方\N{\fs36}Every place he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.75,0:57:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽芬兰 巴芬湾\N{\fs36}Newfoundland. Baffin Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.42,0:57:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉斯哥 利物浦 纳尔维克\N{\fs36}Glasgow. Liverpool. Narvik.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.30,0:58:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和那个Mike船长远走了\N{\fs36}He had gone with that Captain Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.06,0:58:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mike船长和Moran兄弟拖船海上救助公司\N{\fs36}Captain Mike had contracted for three years
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.46,0:58:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签了三年的合同\N{\fs36}with Moran Brothers Tug and Salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.81,0:58:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘旧船\N{\fs36}The old ship had been refitted
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.32,0:58:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用柴油机和绞车改装过\N{\fs36}with a diesel engine and a new sea winch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.77,0:58:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绕过佛罗里达 沿着大西洋海岸航行\N{\fs36}We went around Florida and up the Atlantic seaboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.78,0:58:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船上有7名船员 Mike船长和我\N{\fs36}We were a crew of seven now. Captain Mike and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.28,0:58:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厨师 来自特拉华州威尔明顿市的Prentiss Mayes\N{\fs36}Cookie, Prentiss Mayes from Wilmington, Delaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.74,0:58:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Brody双胞胎 Rick和Vic\N{\fs36}The Brody twins, Rick and Vic,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.25,0:58:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在海上相处得很好 但不知道为什么\N{\fs36}who got along fine at sea but, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.58,0:58:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一回到陆地\N{\fs36}once they were on dry land
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.96,0:58:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就互相看不惯了\N{\fs36}couldn't stand the sight of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.75,0:58:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每8艘船中 有1艘船会永远回不来\N{\fs36}You know, one in every eight boats never returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.42,0:58:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫John Grimm的人 人如其名\N{\fs36}There was John Grimm, who sure fit his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.63,0:58:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有手下在海上失踪了\N{\fs36}All hands lost at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.59,0:58:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自南达科他州的贝尔维迪尔\N{\fs36}From Belvedere, South Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.22,0:58:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有来自北卡罗来纳州山区阿什维尔的Pleasant Curtis\N{\fs36}And Pleasant Curtis from Asheville, Notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.14,0:58:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了自言自语外 从没跟别人说过话\N{\fs36}Never said a word to anyone, except himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.44,0:58:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时常写信给他\N{\fs36}I wrote him constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.94,0:58:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他我受邀参加纽约市\N{\fs36}I told him I had been invited to audition in New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.53,0:59:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国芭蕾舞学院的面试\N{\fs36}for the School of American Ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.28,0:59:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请留下\N{\fs36}Please stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.02,0:59:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.14,0:59:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以留下来\N{\fs36}You can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.67,0:59:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在团里并不出挑\N{\fs36}But I was relegated to the corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.09,0:59:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个跳舞的流浪者\N{\fs36}Another dancing gypsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.76,0:59:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.90,0:59:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见你的时候\N{\fs36}How is it when you showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.47,0:59:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比系船柱大不了多少 还快要进棺材里了\N{\fs36}you were no bigger than a bollard with one foot in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.48,0:59:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 是我喝得太多了\N{\fs36}but now, either I drink a hell of a lot more than I think I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.94,0:59:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你长高了\N{\fs36}or you sprouted?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.49,0:59:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么秘密\N{\fs36}What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.66,0:59:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 船长\N{\fs36}Well, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.03,0:59:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是你喝多了\N{\fs36}you do drink a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.67,0:59:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住在一个有着恢弘名字的小旅馆里 冬宫\N{\fs36}We stayed in a small hotel with a grand name, The Winter Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.00,0:59:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道你在说什么\N{\fs36}You have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.88,1:00:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂鸟可不是一般的鸟\N{\fs36}The hummingbird is not just another bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.09,1:00:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的心率有每分钟1200下\N{\fs36}Its heart rate's 1,200 beats per minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.24,1:00:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的翅膀每秒振动80次\N{\fs36}Its wings beat 80 times a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.19,1:00:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是阻止它扇动翅膀\N{\fs36}If you was to stop their wings from beating,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.86,1:00:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不到10秒内就会死亡\N{\fs36}it would be dead in less than 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.70,1:00:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是一般的鸟\N{\fs36}This is no ordinary bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.03,1:00:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它简直就是奇迹\N{\fs36}This is a frickin' miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.29,1:00:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们用影像放慢翅膀的扇动\N{\fs36}They slowed down their wings with moving pictures,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.88,1:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们猜他们看到了什么\N{\fs36}and you know what they saw?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.54,1:00:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的翅尖是这样的\N{\fs36}Their wingtips are doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道数字8有什么数学意义吗\N{\fs36}You know what the figure eight is the mathematical symbol for?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.22,1:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无穷大\N{\fs36}Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.89,1:00:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无穷大\N{\fs36}Infinity!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.86,1:00:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人 不管他们有什么不同\N{\fs36}Everybody, no matter what differences they had,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.73,1:01:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语言也好 肤色也罢 都有一个共同点\N{\fs36}the languages, the color of their skin, had one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.70,1:01:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每晚都烂醉如泥\N{\fs36}They were drunk every single night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.16,1:01:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三楼 谢谢\N{\fs36}Three, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.79,1:01:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能等一下我们吗 好吗\N{\fs36}Could you hold, dear, for us, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.50,1:01:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 晚上好\N{\fs36}Thank you very much. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.87,1:01:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫Elizabeth Abbott\N{\fs36}Her name was Elizabeth Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.67,1:01:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不漂亮 简单如纸\N{\fs36}She was not beautiful. She was plain as paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.09,1:01:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她在我眼里很美\N{\fs36}But she was pretty as any picture to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.17,1:01:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么\N{\fs36}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.43,1:01:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道 我们有个长期协议\N{\fs36}If you must know, we have a longstanding agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.10,1:01:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不醉不归\N{\fs36}never to go to bed sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.56,1:01:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对吗 亲爱的  - 你说什么就是什么 亲爱的\N{\fs36}- Isn't that right, darling? - Whatever you say, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.06,1:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她丈夫叫Walter Abbott\N{\fs36}Her husband was Walter Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.32,1:01:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是英国贸易代表团在摩尔曼斯克的首席部长\N{\fs36}He was Chief Minister of the British Trade Mission in Murmansk,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.23,1:01:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是个间谍\N{\fs36}and he was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.78,1:01:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的  - 谢谢 亲爱的\N{\fs36}- Darling. - Oh, thank you, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.95,1:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的 钥匙  - 哦 对\N{\fs36}- Key, darling. - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.45,1:01:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一只鞋跟断了\N{\fs36}I broke my heel off one of my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.62,1:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不习惯不穿鞋走路\N{\fs36}I'm not in the habit of walking about in my stocking feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.63,1:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里白昼很长\N{\fs36}They were long days there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.31,1:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但黑夜更长\N{\fs36}And even longer nights.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一晚 我失眠了\N{\fs36}One particular night, I was having trouble sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.48,1:02:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs36}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.86,1:02:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡不着\N{\fs36}I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.50,1:02:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去泡点茶 你想喝点儿吗\N{\fs36}I was gonna make some tea. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.88,1:02:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢\N{\fs36}Oh, no. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.54,1:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加牛奶还是蜂蜜\N{\fs36}Milk? Honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.58,1:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加点蜂蜜 谢谢\N{\fs36}A bit of honey, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.22,1:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不介意蜂蜜里有苍蝇\N{\fs36}I hope you like flies in your honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.09,1:03:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那还是算了\N{\fs36}Oh, perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.61,1:03:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它多浸一会儿可能会更好\N{\fs36}Oh, maybe better to let it steep a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.78,1:03:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浸\N{\fs36}Steep?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.41,1:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浸泡\N{\fs36}Soak.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.74,1:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是 泡茶就该用正确的方式\N{\fs36}I don't know, I mean, there's a proper way of making tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.34,1:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家乡 人们只希望它是热的\N{\fs36}Well, where I'm from, people just want it to be hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.88,1:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 也没错\N{\fs36}Well, quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.89,1:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你现在是海员  - 水手\N{\fs36}- Now, you're a seaman. - A sailor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.39,1:04:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不要觉得我无礼 但我想问\N{\fs36}I hope you won't think me impolite, but I have to ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.22,1:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个年纪当水手不会太老吗\N{\fs36}aren't you a little old to be working on a boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.43,1:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水手没有年龄限制 只要你能胜任这份工作\N{\fs36}There's no age limit, as long as you can do the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.66,1:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失眠吗 谢谢\N{\fs36}And you have trouble sleeping? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.96,1:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前不这样 我一般睡得像婴儿一样沉\N{\fs36}I didn't think I did. I usually sleep like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.25,1:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事让我睡不着\N{\fs36}Something's been keeping me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.92,1:04:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸在他80多岁的时候\N{\fs36}My father, in his 80s,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.21,1:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深信自己会在睡梦中死去\N{\fs36}he was so convinced he was gonna die in his sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.13,1:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只让自己睡午觉\N{\fs36}he limited himself to having afternoon naps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.01,1:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并坚信自己可以骗过死神\N{\fs36}He was so determined he was gonna cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.97,1:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他有吗  - 有什么\N{\fs36}- Did he? - Did he what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.97,1:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在睡梦中死去\N{\fs36}Die in his sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.31,1:05:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他坐在他最爱的椅子上\N{\fs36}He died sitting in his favorite chair
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.98,1:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着他最喜欢的广播死去了\N{\fs36}listening to his favorite program on the wireless.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.73,1:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定预感到了什么\N{\fs36}He must have known something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.95,1:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫是英国贸易部部长\N{\fs36}My husband's the British Trade Minister,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.54,1:05:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来这儿14个月了\N{\fs36}and we've been here for 14 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.12,1:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天啊  - 我们本来要去北京的\N{\fs36}- Good God. - We were supposed to go to Peking
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.54,1:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能永远都去不了了\N{\fs36}but it never seemed to work out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.50,1:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过远东吗\N{\fs36}Have you been in the Far East?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.30,1:05:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 我哪里都没去过\N{\fs36}No. I've never been anywhere, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.59,1:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 海港以外的地方\N{\fs36}I mean, outside of harbors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.14,1:05:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪里来的\N{\fs36}And where is it that you're from?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.89,1:05:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯安那州的新奥尔良\N{\fs36}New Orleans. Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.89,1:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有第二个新奥尔良了\N{\fs36}I didn't know there was another.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她告诉了我\N{\fs36}And she told me about all
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.98,1:05:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去过的所有地方 和她的所见所闻\N{\fs36}the places she had been, and what she had seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.15,1:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直聊到快天亮\N{\fs36}And we talked till just before the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.07,1:05:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己是个酒鬼\N{\fs36}I'm just a lush, myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.66,1:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回到了各自的房间 过各自的生活\N{\fs36}And we went back to our rooms, to our separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.04,1:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每天晚上 我们都会在大厅见面\N{\fs36}But every night, we'd meet again in that lobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.68,1:06:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午夜时分的旅馆是个神奇的地方\N{\fs36}A hotel in the middle of the night can be a magical place.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.43,1:06:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠跑跑停停\N{\fs36}A mouse running, and stopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.77,1:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖气嘶嘶作响\N{\fs36}A radiator hissing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.90,1:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗帘随风呜鸣\N{\fs36}A curtain blowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.53,1:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让人觉得宁静 甚至慰藉\N{\fs36}There's something peaceful, even comforting
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.99,1:06:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你知道所爱之人在床上熟睡\N{\fs36}knowing that the people you love are asleep in their beds
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.33,1:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么能伤害他们\N{\fs36}where nothing can harm them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.67,1:06:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elizabeth和我会忘记时间\N{\fs36}Elizabeth and I would lose track of the night
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.13,1:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到黎明到来\N{\fs36}until just before daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.93,1:06:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我可能让你误解了\N{\fs36}I think I may have given you the wrong impression.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.80,1:07:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs36}Beg pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已婚女人可不会经常在半夜\N{\fs36}Well, married women don't customarily sit around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.35,1:07:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陌生男人坐在旅馆里\N{\fs36}in the middle of the night with strange men in hotels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.48,1:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道已婚女人该做什么 不该做什么\N{\fs36}I wouldn't know what a married woman does or doesn't do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.78,1:07:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs36}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.58,1:07:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩尔曼斯克\N{\fs36}Murmansk.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.50,1:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我遇见了一个人 坠入了爱河"\N{\fs36}"I've met somebody, and I've fallen in love."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.67,1:07:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.71,1:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是60多年前的事了\N{\fs36}That was over 60 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.55,1:07:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱他吗 妈妈\N{\fs36}Did you love him, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.68,1:07:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女孩哪懂什么爱情\N{\fs36}What does a girl know about love?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.05,1:08:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs36}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.76,1:08:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我穿得不得体  - 看起来很好啊 这才是你\N{\fs36}- I'm not dressed. - Oh, you look splendid, just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.81,1:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摩尔曼斯克 不要为\N{\fs36}Don't waste any time bothering
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.11,1:08:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红酒或者奶酪而费心\N{\fs36}about the wine or the cheese in Murmansk,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.97,1:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些实在很平常\N{\fs36}'cause they're really completely ordinary,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.10,1:08:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是鱼子酱和伏特加\N{\fs36}but the caviar and the vodka
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.65,1:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才更丰富奢华\N{\fs36}are sublime and plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.53,1:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那\N{\fs36}So.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细细品尝\N{\fs36}Savor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.54,1:08:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一次都吃光\N{\fs36}And don't eat it all at once,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.63,1:08:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 就没有什么可享受的了\N{\fs36}because that way, there's nothing left to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.30,1:09:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 小咽一口伏特加\N{\fs36}And now, take a little swallow of vodka
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.52,1:09:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着嘴里还有鱼子酱\N{\fs36}while it's still in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.61,1:09:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没和多少女人交往过 对吧\N{\fs36}You haven't been with many women, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.66,1:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天没有过\N{\fs36}Not on Sundays.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.49,1:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没吃过鱼子酱 是吧\N{\fs36}And you've never had caviar before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.33,1:09:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没吃过 女士\N{\fs36}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.79,1:09:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,19岁的时候\N{\fs36}When I was 19,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.46,1:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为第一个\N{\fs36}I attempted to become the first woman
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.96,1:09:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横渡英吉利海峡的女人\N{\fs36}ever to swim the English Channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.56,1:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs36}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.76,1:09:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那天的水流很急\N{\fs36}But the current that day was so strong that,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.93,1:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每划一次 就会被推后两下\N{\fs36}for every stroke I took, I was pushed back two.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.61,1:09:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在水里待了32小时\N{\fs36}I was in the water for 32 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.19,1:10:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我离加来还有2英里时\N{\fs36}And when I was two miles from Calais,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.16,1:10:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始下雨了\N{\fs36}it started to rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.62,1:10:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 稳住\N{\fs36}That's it! Steady on!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.08,1:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在游不动的时候\N{\fs36}When I couldn't go any further,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.29,1:10:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我停下了\N{\fs36}I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.13,1:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这么停下了\N{\fs36}I just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.34,1:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都问我 要再试试吗\N{\fs36}And everybody asked me, would I try again?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.97,1:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不呢\N{\fs36}For why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.72,1:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却没有尝试\N{\fs36}But I never did.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.85,1:10:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上\N{\fs36}As a matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.70,1:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后 我没做过什么\N{\fs36}I've never done anything with my life after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.23,1:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手好粗糙\N{\fs36}Your hands are so coarse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.62,1:10:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到吹向你脸颊的风\N{\fs36}I can feel the wind in your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.96,1:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经午夜了\N{\fs36}I'm afraid it's the Witching hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.35,1:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是第一次有女人吻我\N{\fs36}It was the first time a woman had ever kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.18,1:11:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你永远不会忘记的\N{\fs36}It's something you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.07,1:11:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我觉得我年轻了\N{\fs36}I think you make me feel younger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.20,1:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也让我觉得自己年轻了\N{\fs36}You make me feel years younger, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.87,1:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我还年轻\N{\fs36}I wish I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.45,1:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会改变很多事\N{\fs36}So many things I'd change.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.29,1:11:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会弥补所有的错误\N{\fs36}I'd undo all my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.71,1:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么错误\N{\fs36}What mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.76,1:11:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等待\N{\fs36}I kept waiting, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.55,1:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着做些什么改变现状\N{\fs36}Thinking that I'd do something to change my circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.35,1:11:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做些什么\N{\fs36}Do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.64,1:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逝者如斯 一去不返\N{\fs36}Such an awful waste. You never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.35,1:12:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚度了光阴\N{\fs36}Wasted time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.11,1:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们在一起了\N{\fs36}If we're going to have an affair,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.24,1:12:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天不要看我\N{\fs36}you're never to look at me during the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.74,1:12:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亮前我们要分开\N{\fs36}And we're always to part before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.33,1:12:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说"我爱你"\N{\fs36}And we will never say "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.59,1:12:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是规定\N{\fs36}Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.01,1:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你冷吗  - 冻死了\N{\fs36}- Are you cold? - I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.26,1:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都冻僵了\N{\fs36}Oh, you! You're frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.60,1:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真笨 我穿着皮衣站在这里\N{\fs36}What an idiot, I'm standing here in this fur.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.52,1:12:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考虑得太不周到了\N{\fs36}How thoughtless of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.17,1:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是第一个爱过我的女人\N{\fs36}She was the first woman that ever loved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.97,1:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我跳过一些吗\N{\fs36}You want me to skip some?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.30,1:13:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 我很高兴有人能温暖他\N{\fs36}No, I'm glad he had somebody to keep him warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.73,1:13:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我等不及再见到她了"\N{\fs36}"I couldn't wait to see her again."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.12,1:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每晚都见面\N{\fs36}We saw each other every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.00,1:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开同一个房间\N{\fs36}We always used the same room.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.29,1:13:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每一次都是新鲜的 不同的\N{\fs36}But each time seemed new and different.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.01,1:13:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs36}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.93,1:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elizabeth\N{\fs36}Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.04,1:14:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs36}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.82,1:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到有一晚\N{\fs36}Until one night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.73,1:14:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 1941年12月7日\N{\fs36}Yesterday, December 7th, 1941,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.40,1:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个国耻日里\N{\fs36}a date which will live in infamy...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.61,1:15:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次会议 一次事关未来的政治会议\N{\fs36}It's a meeting, a policy meeting regarding your future,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.70,1:15:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能远不止如此\N{\fs36}possibly beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.66,1:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们 计划有变\N{\fs36}There's been a change of plan, lads.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.42,1:15:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可能知道或不知道\N{\fs36}As you may or may not know,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.13,1:15:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人昨天轰炸了珍珠港\N{\fs36}the Japs bombed Pearl Harbor yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.17,1:15:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frank D. Roosevelt要求我们各司其职\N{\fs36}Frank D. Roosevelt's asked each of us to do our part.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.17,1:15:16.28,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,美国第32任总统
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.13,1:15:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔西号\N{\fs36}The Chelsea's been
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.06,1:15:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被美国海军征用\N{\fs36}commissioned to serve in the United States Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.68,1:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来维修 打捞和救援\N{\fs36}To repair, to salvage, and to rescue.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.48,1:15:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁不想打仗的 现在说出来\N{\fs36}Anybody doesn't want to go to war, now is the time to say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.94,1:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友 一旦你踏上那艘船 你就是海军一员了\N{\fs36}Once you set foot on that boat, you're in the Navy, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.36,1:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mike 我一直想和你谈谈\N{\fs36}Yeah, I've been meaning to talk with you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.49,1:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子身体欠佳\N{\fs36}My wife's doing poorly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.62,1:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再见她一面\N{\fs36}I'd like to maybe see her one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.08,1:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在可以回家了 Mayes先生\N{\fs36}You're free to make your way home any way you can, Mr. Mayes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.51,1:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他走了 谁来做饭呢\N{\fs36}Well, if he's leaving, who's gonna cook?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.38,1:16:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物中毒可是海上人员死亡的主要原因之一啊\N{\fs36}Food poisoning's one of the leading causes of death at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.56,1:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅次于安全设备不足\N{\fs36}Right after inadequate safety equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.02,1:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 我能做饭 我做了一辈子了\N{\fs36}I can cook, Captain. Been doing it all my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.77,1:16:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定 你也不喜欢战争 Benjamin\N{\fs36}I don't know. You're a little moody for war, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.27,1:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过管他呢\N{\fs36}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.32,1:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打倒小日本和德国佬的人\N{\fs36}I'll take any man wants to
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.12,1:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你们一起走\N{\fs36}kick the shite out of the Japs and the Huns.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.07,1:16:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么定了 打包装备 我们要参战了 先生们\N{\fs36}That's it, pack your gear. We're going to war, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.71,1:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她留了纸条\N{\fs36}She had left a note.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.84,1:16:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她写道 "能遇见你真好"\N{\fs36}She wrote, "It was nice to have met you."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.34,1:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已\N{\fs36}And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.18,1:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争和我们想的不一样\N{\fs36}It wasn't the war any of us expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.35,1:16:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是拖走破损的船 其实都是些破铜烂铁\N{\fs36}We would just tow crippled ships, scraps of metal, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.60,1:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有战争 我们也看不到\N{\fs36}If there was a war, we didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.48,1:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派给我们的主炮手非常热爱海军\N{\fs36}There was a man assigned to us. The Chief Gunner loved the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.65,1:17:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是 他热爱美国\N{\fs36}But most of all, he loved America.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.95,1:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上没有其他国家\N{\fs36}There is no other country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.95,1:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你拼写美国\N{\fs36}When you spell America...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.16,1:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫Dennis Smith 是个纯血统的切罗基人\N{\fs36}His name was Dennis Smith, and he was a full-blooded Cherokee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.41,1:17:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的家族在美国居住了500多年\N{\fs36}His family had been Americans for over 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.86,1:17:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些和平主义者说凭良心来讲 他们不会打仗\N{\fs36}These pacifists. They say they won't fight on conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.25,1:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是所有人都凭良心来讲\N{\fs36}Now, where would be if everybody decided to act
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.97,1:17:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那会怎么样  - 小点声 好吗 长官\N{\fs36}- according to their conscience? - Keep it down, would you, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.15,1:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 我一直在观察你\N{\fs36}Hey. I've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.70,1:17:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来挺可信\N{\fs36}You seem trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.29,1:17:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果天有不测\N{\fs36}If something happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.46,1:17:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我把这个给我老婆吗\N{\fs36}could you see that this gets to my wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.13,1:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把他的工钱都给了我 他一分钱都没花\N{\fs36}He'd given me all of his pay. Hadn't spent a dime of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.59,1:18:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让家人知道 我惦记着他们\N{\fs36}I want my family to know I was thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.60,1:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人到甲板上\N{\fs36}All hands on deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.94,1:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚上来 你们这些懒货\N{\fs36}Get your asses up here, you lazy bastards!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.05,1:18:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争最终还是来了\N{\fs36}The war had finally found us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.97,1:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来\N{\fs36}All stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.14,1:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pleasant 转一下那个灯\N{\fs36}Pleasant, man that light.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.02,1:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一艘载有1300人的运输舰被鱼雷击沉了\N{\fs36}A transport carrying 1,300 men had been split by a torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.61,1:19:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是第一个到达现场的\N{\fs36}We were first to arrive at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.99,1:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 关掉引擎  - 停下来\N{\fs36}- Cut the engines! - All stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.67,1:19:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海上只有我们的声音\N{\fs36}We were the only sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.52,1:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\fs36}Fellas!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.90,1:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水艇\N{\fs36}Sub!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.78,1:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝对跑不过这群人\N{\fs36}We sure as hell can't outrun them fuckers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.33,1:19:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位\N{\fs36}Battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.51,1:20:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 长官\N{\fs36}Thank you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.72,1:20:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs36}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.90,1:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一个吗\N{\fs36}Is that the last one?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.32,1:21:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长\N{\fs36}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.17,1:22:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的把我的纹身打烂了\N{\fs36}They shot the hell out of my painting!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.09,1:22:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我握着你的手\N{\fs36}Give me your other hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.30,1:22:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会没事的 船长\N{\fs36}You'll be all right, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.43,1:22:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在天堂给你留了个好位置呢\N{\fs36}They got a nice spot in Heaven waiting for you. Nice spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.23,1:22:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于生活的现状 你可以像疯狗一样不满\N{\fs36}You can be as mad as a mad dog at the way things went.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.27,1:22:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以破口大骂 可以诅咒命运\N{\fs36}You could swear, curse the Fates.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.24,1:22:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到了生命尽头\N{\fs36}But when it comes to the end,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.58,1:22:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是得放手\N{\fs36}you have to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.34,1:22:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长\N{\fs36}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.40,1:23:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 1328个人失去了生命\N{\fs36}Thirteen hundred and twenty eight men died that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.03,1:23:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟切罗基人Dennis Smith道了永别\N{\fs36}I said my goodbyes to the Cherokee, Dennis Smith.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.24,1:23:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有John Grimm 他说得没错 他将葬身大海\N{\fs36}John Grimm, who was right, he was gonna die there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.91,1:23:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把Pleasant Curtis的钱寄给了他的妻子\N{\fs36}I sent Pleasant Curtis' wife his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.46,1:23:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向双胞胎的Vic Brody道了别\N{\fs36}I said goodbye to the twin, Vic Brody,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.63,1:23:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Mike Clark 切尔西号的船长\N{\fs36}and to Mike Clark, captain of the tugboat Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.76,1:23:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那些怀揣着梦想的人道了别\N{\fs36}I said goodbye to all the other men who had dreams of their own,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.35,1:23:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有人想做保险推销员\N{\fs36}all the men who wanted to be insurance salesmen
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.02,1:23:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想做医生 律师 还有印第安酋长\N{\fs36}or doctors or lawyers or Indian chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.02,1:23:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个修不好了\N{\fs36}This don't get fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.94,1:23:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 死亡不再是自然而然的了\N{\fs36}Out here, death didn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.00,1:24:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没在这么远的海上见过蜂鸟\N{\fs36}I'd never seen a hummingbird that far out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.72,1:24:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前没有 之后也没有了\N{\fs36}Before or since.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.18,1:24:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1945年5月 那年我26岁\N{\fs36}And in May of 1945, when I was 26 years old,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.52,1:24:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回到了家\N{\fs36}I came home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.57,1:24:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好了 好了\N{\fs36}I'm ready! I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.28,1:24:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fs36}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.53,1:24:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我好了  - 好了 我来了 Alfalina小姐\N{\fs36}- I'm ready! - All right, I'm coming, Miss Alfalina.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.28,1:24:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Queenie  - 怎么了\N{\fs36}- Queenie? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.67,1:24:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊 你回家了 你居然回来了\N{\fs36}Sweet Jesus! Oh, you're home! Oh, Lord, you came back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.46,1:25:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 让我好好看看你  - 妈妈 那是谁啊\N{\fs36}- Let me look at you. - Who's that, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.64,1:25:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 这是你哥哥 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Child, it's your brother, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.54,1:25:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道我还有哥哥\N{\fs36}I didn't know he was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.84,1:25:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 你不知道的事情太多了\N{\fs36}There's a shitload of things you don't know, child.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.74,1:25:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧去把地扫完\N{\fs36}Get on out there and finish sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.12,1:25:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过来洗手 帮我摆餐桌 快去\N{\fs36}Come here, wash your hands, help me with the table. Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.18,1:25:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过来 你看起来跟重生了一样\N{\fs36}Turn around. You look like you've been born again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.19,1:25:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比春天还有活力\N{\fs36}Younger than the springtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.52,1:25:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牧师施法的时候 肯定给了你第二条生命\N{\fs36}I think that preacher laid hands on you gave you a second life.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.28,1:25:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你的时候就知道 你与众不同\N{\fs36}I knew it that moment I saw you, you were special.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.03,1:25:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说 我膝盖老疼\N{\fs36}I tell you what, my knees are sore,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.14,1:25:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我每晚都跪着祈祷上帝\N{\fs36}'cause I've been on them every night asking the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.62,1:25:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 "上帝啊 我只求他平安回家"\N{\fs36}I said, "God, just bring him home safely."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.46,1:25:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得我跟你说的吗\N{\fs36}Remember what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.04,1:25:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"世事难料"\N{\fs36}"You never know what's coming for you?"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.79,1:25:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 快坐下\N{\fs36}That's right. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.09,1:25:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么有意思的事情说来听听\N{\fs36}Well, you learn anything worth repeating?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.30,1:25:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的确经历了不少  - 你尝过了苦头\N{\fs36}- I sure saw some things. - Oh, you seen some pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.06,1:25:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不过也有甜头  - 没错 是的\N{\fs36}- Some joy, too? - Sure. Sure, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.10,1:25:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想听你说这些 看看你啊\N{\fs36}Yeah, that's what I want to hear. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.15,1:26:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Tizzy呢  - 哦 孩子\N{\fs36}- Where's Tizzy? - Oh, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.11,1:26:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Weathers先生去年四月在睡梦中走了\N{\fs36}Mr. Weathers died in his sleep one night last April.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.08,1:26:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 妈妈 真遗憾  - 孩子 不用担心\N{\fs36}- Mama, I'm so sorry. - Don't you worry about that, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.29,1:26:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在活着的 也就一两个了\N{\fs36}Yeah, well, it's only one or two of them left now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.04,1:26:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过都还挺快活\N{\fs36}They all just about new.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.78,1:26:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该跟别人一样 都等着那一天吧\N{\fs36}Guess they're waiting their turn like everybody else, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.59,1:26:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回来我真是太高兴了\N{\fs36}I'm so glad you're back home with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.43,1:26:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我们得给你\N{\fs36}Now, we're gonna have to
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找个妻子和一份新工作 就这么定了\N{\fs36}find you a wife and a new job! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.98,1:26:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来 帮我摆桌子\N{\fs36}Come on in here, help me with this table.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.73,1:26:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.46,1:26:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 你这是在浪费时间 她聋透了\N{\fs36}You're wasting your time, baby. She's stone deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.65,1:26:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在DeSeroux太太以前住的房间\N{\fs36}Oh, and you'll be staying in what was Mrs. DeSeroux's old room.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.78,1:26:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了 不能和别人挤一间了\N{\fs36}You're too big to be rooming with anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.82,1:26:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家的感觉很奇妙\N{\fs36}It's a funny thing about coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.12,1:26:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子没变 气味没变 感觉没变\N{\fs36}Looks the same, smells the same, feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.63,1:27:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有告诉过你 我曾被闪电击中了7次\N{\fs36}Did I ever tell you I've been struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.13,1:27:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次是我开着我的车\N{\fs36}Once when I was sitting in my truck,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.00,1:27:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里想着自己的事\N{\fs36}just minding my own business.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.35,1:27:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才意识到 只有你自己变了\N{\fs36}You realize what's changed is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.48,1:27:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来不久后的一个早晨\N{\fs36}And late one morning, not long after I'd been back...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.90,1:27:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.34,1:27:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs36}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.97,1:27:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不好意思 请问Queenie在吗  - Daisy\N{\fs36}- Excuse me, is Queenie here? - Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.76,1:28:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是我 Benjamin啊  - Benjamin\N{\fs36}- It's me, Benjamin. - Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.95,1:28:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs36}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.20,1:28:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是你 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Of course it's you! Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.20,1:28:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近好吗 好久没见了\N{\fs36}How are you? It's been such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.32,1:28:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道的太多了 你什么时候回来的\N{\fs36}There's so much I want to know. When did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.04,1:28:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几周前回来的\N{\fs36}Well, I got back a few weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.72,1:28:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问Queenie了\N{\fs36}I spoke to Queenie,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.92,1:28:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说你在打仗 在海上的什么地方\N{\fs36}she said you were in the war, somewhere at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.63,1:28:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们特别 特别担心你  - 我没事\N{\fs36}- We were so, so worried about you. - Oh, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.47,1:28:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你啊 你真好看\N{\fs36}Well, look at you. You're so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.14,1:28:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你后来就没给我写信了\N{\fs36}You stopped writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.02,1:28:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我离开的时候 她还是个小女孩\N{\fs36}"When I had left, she was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.00,1:28:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现如今 已经成为了窈窕淑女\N{\fs36}And a woman had taken her place.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.44,1:28:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我见过的最美的女人"\N{\fs36}She was the most beautiful woman I'd ever seen."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.74,1:28:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美\N{\fs36}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.24,1:28:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"最美"\N{\fs36}"The most beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.87,1:28:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你还记得Fuller奶奶吗  - 记得啊 怎么了\N{\fs36}- You remember Grandma Fuller? - Why, sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.71,1:29:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她去世了  - 我听说了 节哀吧\N{\fs36}- She passed. - I heard that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.06,1:29:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信我们在这里见面了 真是缘分\N{\fs36}I just can't believe we're both here. Must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.70,1:29:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 他们把这个叫做什么\N{\fs36}No, no, what do they call it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.63,1:29:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运\N{\fs36}Kismet.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.13,1:29:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道Edgar Cayce吗 那个灵媒\N{\fs36}Do you know about Edgar Cayce, the psychic?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.38,1:29:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我不\N{\fs36}I don't believe I...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.34,1:29:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说万事已经命中注定\N{\fs36}He says that everything is predetermined,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.22,1:29:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我更觉得这是缘分\N{\fs36}but I like to think of it as fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.77,1:29:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道缘分是怎么回事 但我很高兴这一切发生了\N{\fs36}I'm not sure how it works, but I'm glad it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.11,1:29:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过曼哈顿吗 在我住处的河对岸\N{\fs36}Have you been to Manhattan? It's right across the river from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.00,1:29:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我站在床上\N{\fs36}Now, I can see the Empire State Building
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.22,1:29:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以看见帝国大厦\N{\fs36}if I stand on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.06,1:29:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢 你去了哪些地方\N{\fs36}What about you? Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.14,1:29:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都说来我听听 上次你写信说\N{\fs36}Tell me everything. Last time you wrote,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.11,1:29:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去俄罗斯了\N{\fs36}you said you'd been to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.75,1:29:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想去俄罗斯 那里真有别人说的那么冷吗\N{\fs36}I've always wanted to go to Russia. Is it as cold as they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.00,1:29:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 冷得多呢  - 我的天\N{\fs36}- Twice as cold. - My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.38,1:29:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都说你不一样 但我是真心觉得你与众不同\N{\fs36}We always said you were different. But I think you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.14,1:29:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你遇见了喜欢的人 有结果吗\N{\fs36}You wrote that you met somebody. Did it work out?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.18,1:30:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是分道扬镳了\N{\fs36}It ran its course.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.23,1:30:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你还记得这个吗\N{\fs36}Hey, do you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.12,1:30:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这是一只老袋鼠下午5点的样子"\N{\fs36}"This is the picture of Old Man Kangaroo at 5 in the afternoon."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.91,1:30:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃个晚饭吧\N{\fs36}Would you like to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.63,1:30:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有告诉过你 我跟着Balanchine跳舞啊\N{\fs36}Did I tell you that I danced for Balanchine?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.63,1:30:34.55,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,美国舞蹈家 编导
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.22,1:30:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个著名的编舞家 他说我的曲线很完美\N{\fs36}Oh, he's a famous choreographer. He said that I had perfect line.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.47,1:30:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次排练 有人摔倒了\N{\fs36}You know, in a rehearsal once, a dancer fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.10,1:30:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他就 把这个动作编进舞蹈里了\N{\fs36}And he just... He just put it right into the production.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.02,1:30:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗 在一段经典芭蕾舞里\N{\fs36}I mean, can you imagine that? Like in a... In a classical ballet?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.76,1:30:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让舞者故意摔倒\N{\fs36}You know, a dancer, intentionally falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.10,1:30:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今有个全新的词来形容舞蹈了 叫"抽象"\N{\fs36}There's a whole new word for dance now. It's called "Abstract."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.70,1:31:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不止他一个人这么做了\N{\fs36}No, he's not the only one, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.12,1:31:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Lincoln Kirstein和Lucia Chase 对了\N{\fs36}There's Lincoln Kirstein and Lucia Chase, and oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.12,1:31:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Agnes de Mille\N{\fs36}Oh, there's Agnes de Mille.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.71,1:31:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她打破了常规\N{\fs36}She's just torn up all those conventions,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.88,1:31:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是挺胸抬头那一套\N{\fs36}you know, all that straight-up-and-down stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.96,1:31:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞蹈不是循规蹈矩\N{\fs36}It's not about the formality of the dance,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.67,1:31:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是舞者的感觉\N{\fs36}it's about what the dancer's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.26,1:31:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟我说的这个全新的世界\N{\fs36}As she told me about this big new world,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.05,1:31:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些我从未听过的名字\N{\fs36}names that didn't mean a thing to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.68,1:31:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说的话 我没听进去多少\N{\fs36}I didn't really hear very much of what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.14,1:31:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切是全新的 现代的 美式的\N{\fs36}It's new and it's modern and it's American.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.18,1:31:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们了解我们的活力和形体\N{\fs36}They understand our vigor and our physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.44,1:31:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 我一直在说一直在说\N{\fs36}Oh, my God. I've just been talking and talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.69,1:31:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 我喜欢听你说 我不知道你还抽烟\N{\fs36}No, no, I've enjoyed listening. I didn't know you smoked.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.28,1:31:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经长大了\N{\fs36}I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.20,1:31:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大到还可以做很多别的\N{\fs36}I'm old enough for a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.62,1:31:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纽约 我们整晚不睡\N{\fs36}In New York, we stay up all night,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.33,1:31:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着太阳爬上仓库屋顶\N{\fs36}watch the sun come up over the warehouses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.46,1:31:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总能找些事情做\N{\fs36}There's always something to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.44,1:32:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天就要回去了\N{\fs36}I have to go back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.74,1:32:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这么快  - 我也想留下来\N{\fs36}- So soon. - Wish I could stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.66,1:32:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞者已经不需要服装和布景了\N{\fs36}Dancers don't need costumes or scenery anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.96,1:32:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都能想到自己裸身跳舞的样子\N{\fs36}I can imagine dancing completely naked.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.79,1:32:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看过D.H.Lawrence的书吗\N{\fs36}Have you read D. H. Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.79,1:32:34.38,电影注释,NTP,0,0,0,,英国作家 作品过多描写色情
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.25,1:32:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 呃  - 他的书被禁了\N{\fs36}- Well... - His books were banned.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.46,1:32:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读他的书就像在做爱\N{\fs36}The words are like making love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.68,1:33:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舞团里 大家必须相互信任\N{\fs36}In our company, we have to trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.40,1:33:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性也是其中的一部分\N{\fs36}Sex is a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.64,1:33:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多舞者都是女同性恋\N{\fs36}You know, a lot of the dancers are lesbians.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.54,1:33:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个女人想和我睡\N{\fs36}There was one woman who wanted to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.92,1:34:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你会不高兴吗  - 关于哪个部分\N{\fs36}- Does that upset you? - Which part?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.05,1:34:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想跟我睡\N{\fs36}Somebody wanting to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.01,1:34:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很吸引人\N{\fs36}You're a desirable woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.50,1:34:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 大多数人都想和你睡吧\N{\fs36}I would think most of them would want to sleep with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.10,1:34:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧\N{\fs36}Let's go back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.14,1:34:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者开个房\N{\fs36}Or we could get a room somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.52,1:34:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我可以脱下你的夹克  - 这样不好吧 Daisy\N{\fs36}- We could lay down your jacket. - I don't know, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.82,1:34:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我不想还是怎么的\N{\fs36}It's not that I wouldn't like to or anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.92,1:34:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕我会让你失望\N{\fs36}I think I'll just disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.08,1:34:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 我和更老的人都在一起过\N{\fs36}Oh, Benjamin, I've been with older men.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.95,1:34:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明早就回纽约了\N{\fs36}You're going back to New York in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.08,1:34:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该和你朋友在一起\N{\fs36}You should be with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.42,1:34:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你只能年轻一次  - 我已经够大了\N{\fs36}- You're only young once. - Oh, I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.18,1:34:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy 今晚不行\N{\fs36}Daisy, just not tonight, is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.15,1:34:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以去听听音乐\N{\fs36}We could go hear some music.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.57,1:35:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的生命因机遇而有意义\N{\fs36}Our lives are defined by opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.11,1:35:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至包括我们错过的\N{\fs36}Even the ones we miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.07,1:35:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你英俊潇洒 风度翩翩\N{\fs36}You look so handsome and so distinguished.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.70,1:35:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说飓风不会来了 刚好从这儿刮走\N{\fs36}They're saying the hurricane's gonna miss us, blow right on by.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.95,1:35:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那太好了  - 我要和妈妈一起在毯子下面躺着\N{\fs36}- Oh, that's great. - I'll stay under the blankets with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.72,1:35:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么也没说 Benjamin\N{\fs36}She says nothing... Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.67,1:35:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我的生活 又发生了不一样的"\N{\fs36}"Things were becoming different..."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.04,1:35:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变化\N{\fs36}...for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.34,1:35:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的白发褪去 黑发像野草一样生长\N{\fs36}My hair had very little gray and grew like weeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.00,1:35:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的嗅觉更灵敏 听力也更敏锐\N{\fs36}My sense of smell was keener. My hearing, more acute.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.68,1:35:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走得更快更远\N{\fs36}I could walk further and faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.44,1:35:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当所有人都在老去 我却独自返老还童\N{\fs36}While everybody else was aging, I was getting younger, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.24,1:35:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs36}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.86,1:35:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.28,1:35:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还记得我吗  - 当然了 Button先生\N{\fs36}- Do you remember me? - Well, sure I do, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.08,1:35:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你怎么了  - 脚感染了 那个\N{\fs36}- What happened to you? - Darn foot. Got infected, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.33,1:36:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 朋友\N{\fs36}Welcome home, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.42,1:36:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是喜欢把萨泽拉克和威士忌混起来喝啊\N{\fs36}I see you're still drinking your Sazerac with whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.47,1:36:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯了\N{\fs36}Creature of habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.04,1:36:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还去波旁大道那边的房子吗\N{\fs36}You still visiting the house on Bourbon Street?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.01,1:36:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没去了\N{\fs36}Not for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.35,1:36:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来有意思\N{\fs36}Interesting times, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.52,1:36:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从每天做4万个纽扣\N{\fs36}We went from making 40,000
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.86,1:36:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在一天做50万\N{\fs36}to nearly half a million buttons a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.06,1:36:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇佣的员工是以前的10倍\N{\fs36}We employed 10 times the number of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.19,1:36:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们日以继夜地赶工\N{\fs36}We were operating around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.24,1:36:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来惭愧\N{\fs36}Damn shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.92,1:36:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争让纽扣生意更好了\N{\fs36}The war has been kind to the button industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.41,1:36:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\fs36}You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.04,1:36:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我病了 不知道还能活多久\N{\fs36}I'm sick. I don't know how much longer I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.64,1:36:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我很抱歉 Button先生  - 不用这么说\N{\fs36}- I'm sorry to hear that, Mr. Button. - No...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.72,1:36:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么朋友 习惯独来独往\N{\fs36}I don't have any people. I keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.26,1:36:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不要介意 但是如果可能的话\N{\fs36}I hope you don't mind, but, whenever possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.39,1:36:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能陪着我\N{\fs36}I'd enjoy your company.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.48,1:37:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力而为的\N{\fs36}I'll certainly do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.27,1:37:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 你了解纽扣生意吗\N{\fs36}Benjamin, do you know anything about buttons?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.78,1:37:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 Button纽扣生意已经在家族中传承了124年了\N{\fs36}Now, Button's Buttons has been in our family for 124 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.08,1:37:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷是位裁缝 在里士满开了间小铺子\N{\fs36}My grandfather was a tailor, and he had a small shop in Richmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.79,1:37:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内战之后 他搬去了新奥尔良\N{\fs36}After the Civil War, he moved to New Orleans,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.42,1:37:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 我爸爸凭借聪明才智 开始经营纽扣生意\N{\fs36}where my father had the wisdom to make our own buttons.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.68,1:37:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他的经营下 裁缝铺扩张到了现在的规模\N{\fs36}So, with his help, the tailor shop grew to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.22,1:37:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在 我连线都不会缝\N{\fs36}And today, I can't sew a stitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.12,1:37:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这故事很有意思\N{\fs36}That's very, very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.94,1:37:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您自己做得也很好啊\N{\fs36}You sure have done well for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.20,1:37:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我能帮你什么呢 Button先生\N{\fs36}So, what can I do for you, Mr. Button?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.79,1:38:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin 你是我的儿子\N{\fs36}Benjamin? You're my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.44,1:38:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我之前没有告诉你\N{\fs36}I'm so sorry I never told you before.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.38,1:38:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生在大战结束的那一晚\N{\fs36}You were born the night the Great War ended.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.43,1:38:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈难产而死\N{\fs36}Your mother died giving birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.64,1:38:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你是个怪物\N{\fs36}I thought you were a monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.40,1:38:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你妈妈保证过 会让你平安\N{\fs36}I promised your mother I'd make sure you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.12,1:38:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不该抛弃你\N{\fs36}I should never have abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.67,1:38:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈\N{\fs36}My mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.38,1:38:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在庞恰特雷恩湖边的避暑别墅\N{\fs36}At the summer house on Lake Pontchartrain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.42,1:38:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小的时候 喜欢比别人起得都早\N{\fs36}When I was a boy, I'd love to wake up before anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.97,1:38:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到湖边 迎接新一天的到来\N{\fs36}run down to that lake and watch the day begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.64,1:39:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我觉得自己是世界上唯一的生命\N{\fs36}It was as if I was the only one alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.10,1:39:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她一见钟情\N{\fs36}I fell in love the first time I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.36,1:39:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈叫Caroline Murphy\N{\fs36}Your mother's name was Caroline Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.65,1:39:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在你爷爷的厨房里工作\N{\fs36}She worked in your grandfather's kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.78,1:39:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来自都柏林\N{\fs36}She's from Dublin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.12,1:39:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1903年 Caroline和\N{\fs36}In 1903, Caroline and all
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.74,1:39:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她所有兄弟姐妹\N{\fs36}her brothers and sisters came to live here,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.62,1:39:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来新奥尔良生活\N{\fs36}in New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.29,1:39:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会找理由下到厨房\N{\fs36}I'd find excuses to go down to that kitchen
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.14,1:39:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能看到她\N{\fs36}just so I could look at her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.47,1:39:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1918年4月25日 是我人生中最幸福的一天\N{\fs36}April 25th, 1918. Happiest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.98,1:39:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 我娶了你的妈妈\N{\fs36}The day I married your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.94,1:39:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不早告诉我呢\N{\fs36}Why didn't you just tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.94,1:39:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把我所有财产都留给你\N{\fs36}I plan on leaving everything I have to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.32,1:39:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要走了  - 去哪儿\N{\fs36}- I have to go. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.82,1:40:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家\N{\fs36}Home.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.91,1:40:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底怎么想的\N{\fs36}And what does he think, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.52,1:40:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他觉得自己这么冒出来\N{\fs36}He thinks he can just show up
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.90,1:40:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后所有事情就柳暗花明了\N{\fs36}and everything's supposed to be fine and dandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.90,1:40:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大家就能和和气气了\N{\fs36}Everybody's just supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.42,1:40:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事儿他肯定不能如意\N{\fs36}Well, he got another thing coming, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.42,1:40:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天有眼 这事儿他绝对不能如意\N{\fs36}God be my witness, he got another thing coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.92,1:40:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到你的那晚 他只留了18美元\N{\fs36}He left us $18 that night you was found.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.28,1:40:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18张烂票子\N{\fs36}Eighteen ratty dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.01,1:40:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还有块脏兮兮的尿布  - 晚安 妈妈\N{\fs36}- and a filthy diaper. - Good night, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.10,1:40:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 孩子\N{\fs36}Good night, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.57,1:40:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有告诉过你 我曾被闪电击中了7次\N{\fs36}Did I ever tell you I was struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.70,1:40:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次 我在路上遛狗\N{\fs36}Once, I was walking my dog down the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.98,1:40:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我一只眼瞎了 听力也衰退了\N{\fs36}I'm blind in the one eye, can't hardly hear,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.84,1:40:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙地抽搐 发抖\N{\fs36}get twitches and shakes out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.98,1:41:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也总是记不住东西\N{\fs36}always losing my line of thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.32,1:41:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道吗\N{\fs36}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.47,1:41:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝一直在提醒我 活着就很幸运了\N{\fs36}God keeps reminding me I'm lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.15,1:41:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨要来了\N{\fs36}Storm's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.64,1:41:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 需要帮助吗 上楼第一间卧室\N{\fs36}May I help you, sir? Up the stairs, first bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.97,1:41:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.90,1:42:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs36}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.70,1:42:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你穿上衣服\N{\fs36}Let's get you dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.98,1:42:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦了\N{\fs36}Now that's something.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.90,1:42:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.42,1:43:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于生活的现状 你可以像疯狗一样不满\N{\fs36}You can be mad as a mad dog at the way things went.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.47,1:43:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以破口大骂 可以诅咒命运\N{\fs36}You can swear and curse the Fates.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.47,1:43:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到了生命尽头\N{\fs36}But when it comes to the end,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.93,1:43:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是得放手\N{\fs36}you have to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.78,1:44:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这葬礼很体面\N{\fs36}Well, it sure is a beautiful service.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.14,1:44:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会被葬在你妈妈的旁边\N{\fs36}He'll be buried right next to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.38,1:44:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是我妈妈\N{\fs36}You're my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.84,1:44:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子\N{\fs36}My baby-
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.68,1:44:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没来过纽约\N{\fs36}Now, I'd never seen New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.02,1:46:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不好意思 我是Daisy的朋友  - 这边请\N{\fs36}- Excuse me, I'm a friend of Daisy's. - Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.45,1:46:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Daisy有人找 Daisy  - 来了\N{\fs36}- Daisy has company. Daisy! Daisy! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.20,1:46:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们需要服装  - 谁找我\N{\fs36}- We need the wardrobe. -ls somebody looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.08,1:46:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Benjamin  - 嗨\N{\fs36}- Benjamin. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.59,1:46:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你来这里干什么  - 想着来看看\N{\fs36}- What are you doing here? - Thought I'd come visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.46,1:46:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以 想陪陪你\N{\fs36}Spend some time with you, if I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.01,1:46:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你提前打个电话就好了 你让我措手不及\N{\fs36}Oh, well, I wish you would've called. You took me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.27,1:46:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你可以把花扔了  - 不会的 很好看 谢谢\N{\fs36}- You can just throw them out. - No. Thank you, they're lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.22,1:46:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚一直在看你\N{\fs36}I couldn't take my eyes off of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.59,1:46:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太让我着迷了\N{\fs36}I thought you were mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.86,1:46:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么说\N{\fs36}Thank you. That's very kind of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.99,1:47:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去换衣服了 等会儿我们要去派对\N{\fs36}I better get changed. A group of us are going to a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.16,1:47:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你想来吗  - 我听说有家餐厅不错\N{\fs36}- Would you want to come? - Someone told me about a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.50,1:47:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你可能会喜欢\N{\fs36}I thought you might enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.88,1:47:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一 我还订座了\N{\fs36}I made a reservation, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.50,1:47:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的舞者演出后都会去聚聚\N{\fs36}Just, all the dancers go out after the show. You're...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.59,1:47:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我们一起来吧 我去换衣服 好吗\N{\fs36}You're welcome to come with us. I'll get changed. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.85,1:47:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还给俄罗斯芭蕾舞团排过舞\N{\fs36}She choreographs for the Ballets Russes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.06,1:47:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她太厉害了\N{\fs36}She's divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.02,1:47:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真美\N{\fs36}You were breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.53,1:47:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs36}Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.95,1:47:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是David 他也是舞团的\N{\fs36}This is David. He dances with the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.83,1:47:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是Benjamin  - 谁\N{\fs36}- This is Benjamin. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.95,1:47:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我跟你说过的  - 哦对 你好吗\N{\fs36}- I told you about him. - Oh, yeah. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.29,1:47:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我去给你拿杯喝的  - 好 谢谢\N{\fs36}- I'll go get you a drink. - All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.47,1:48:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是她奶奶的朋友\N{\fs36}So, you were a friend of her grandmother's?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.72,1:48:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是什么\N{\fs36}Or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.81,1:48:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fs36}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.89,1:48:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了\N{\fs36}Hey, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.79,1:48:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧\N{\fs36}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.40,1:48:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs36}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.58,1:48:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不知道你会来\N{\fs36}Now, I had no idea you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.95,1:49:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Lord, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.12,1:49:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我怎么样呢 想让我放下这一切吗\N{\fs36}What did you expect? What, you want me to drop everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.14,1:49:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的生活\N{\fs36}Now, this is my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.12,1:49:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 去市区吗\N{\fs36}Babe! You going downtown?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.55,1:49:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 你会玩得很开心的\N{\fs36}Come on. You'll have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.51,1:49:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有很多音乐家和有趣的人\N{\fs36}There's lots of musicians, interestig people.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.14,1:49:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 这都是我的错\N{\fs36}You don't have to do that. This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.14,1:49:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该提前打电话的\N{\fs36}I should've called.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.64,1:49:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着我过来\N{\fs36}I thought I'd come here
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.56,1:49:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给你一个惊喜呢\N{\fs36}and sweep you off your feet or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.82,1:49:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Daisy 快来 走了  - 马上来\N{\fs36}- Daisy! Come on! Let's go. - Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.26,1:49:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他人不错\N{\fs36}Seems nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.82,1:49:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱他吗\N{\fs36}Do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.54,1:49:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱吧\N{\fs36}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.04,1:49:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你高兴\N{\fs36}I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.88,1:49:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回家见吧\N{\fs36}Maybe I'll see you at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.38,1:50:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.51,1:50:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢你的演出\N{\fs36}I enjoyed the show!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.89,1:50:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来是想告诉我 他父亲死了\N{\fs36}He came to tell me his father had died.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.16,1:50:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你也预料不到的  - 我那时才23  什么都不在乎\N{\fs36}- You couldn't have known. - I was 23. I... I just didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.88,1:50:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你做了什么\N{\fs36}What did you do next?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.12,1:50:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些照片 我记得在包的前袋里\N{\fs36}Some photographs, I think, in the front of my bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.17,1:50:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时是个挺不错的舞者\N{\fs36}I was as good a dancer as I was ever gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.18,1:50:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么5年 我\N{\fs36}For five years, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.89,1:50:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在世界各地表演\N{\fs36}I danced everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.10,1:50:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦敦 维也纳 布拉格\N{\fs36}London, Vienna, Prague.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.23,1:50:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过这些照片\N{\fs36}I've never seen these.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.40,1:51:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.78,1:51:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从没说过你的舞蹈生涯\N{\fs36}You never talked about your dancing.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.57,1:51:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是唯一一个受邀\N{\fs36}Well, I was the only American
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.70,1:51:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和莫斯科大剧院芭蕾舞团共舞的美国人 宝贝\N{\fs36}to be invited to dance with the Bolshoi, sugar.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.50,1:51:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了\N{\fs36}It was glorious.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.04,1:51:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从没忘记Benjamin\N{\fs36}But Benjamin was never far from my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.85,1:51:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会不自觉地说\N{\fs36}And I'd find myself saying...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.74,1:51:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.31,1:51:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- "晚安 Daisy"   - 他也这么说\N{\fs36}- "Good night, Daisy." - He said that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.11,1:51:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"生活并不是那么错综复杂\N{\fs36}"Life wasn't all that complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.40,1:51:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是愿意 你也可以说我是在寻找"\N{\fs36}If you want, you might say I was looking for something."
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.60,1:52:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin La Tourneau太太去世了\N{\fs36}Benjamin? Mrs. La Tourneau just passed.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.26,1:52:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 有Benjamin Button先生的信  - 我就是\N{\fs36}- Letter for Mr. Benjamin Button? - That'd be me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.35,1:52:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.00,1:52:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找Daisy Fuller小姐\N{\fs36}Miss Daisy Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.00,1:52:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 稍等 请坐一会儿  - 好的\N{\fs36}- Just a minute. Please have a seat. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.30,1:52:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候 我们的人生会与别人的碰撞\N{\fs36}Sometimes we're on a collision course
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.88,1:52:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我们不知道而已\N{\fs36}and we just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.27,1:53:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是意外 还是注定\N{\fs36}Whether it's by accident or by design,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.34,1:53:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都无法改变\N{\fs36}there's not a thing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.61,1:53:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位在巴黎的女子要出门购物\N{\fs36}A woman in Paris was on her way to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.18,1:53:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她忘了带外套 于是就回去拿\N{\fs36}But she had forgotten her coat, went back to get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.87,1:53:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她拿上了外套 电话响了\N{\fs36}When she had gotten her coat, the phone had rung.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.24,1:53:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她接起电话 聊了一会儿\N{\fs36}So she had stopped to answer it and talked for a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.66,1:53:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女子打电话时\N{\fs36}While the woman was on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.54,1:53:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy正在为巴黎歌剧院的演出做彩排\N{\fs36}Daisy was rehearsing for a performance at the Paris Opera House.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.84,1:53:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩排时 这个女子挂了电话\N{\fs36}And while she was rehearsing, the woman, off the phone now,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.72,1:53:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门打出租车\N{\fs36}had gone outside to get a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.56,1:53:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车司机送完了上一位客人\N{\fs36}Now, a taxi driver had dropped off a fare earlier,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.14,1:53:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车去买咖啡\N{\fs36}and had stopped to get a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.58,1:53:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 Daisy还在排练\N{\fs36}And all the while, Daisy was rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.82,1:53:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位刚送完了客人\N{\fs36}And this cab driver, who dropped off the earlier fare
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.40,1:53:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车去买咖啡的司机\N{\fs36}and had stopped to get the cup of coffee,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.49,1:53:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰好接到了要去购物的女子\N{\fs36}he picked up the lady who was going shopping
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.54,1:53:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 那位女子错过了上一辆出租车\N{\fs36}and had missed getting the earlier cab.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.06,1:54:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个男人过马路 车子只好停下\N{\fs36}The taxi had to stop for a man crossing the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.66,1:54:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人比平时晚起了5分钟\N{\fs36}who had left for work five minutes later than he normally did
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.54,1:54:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他忘了上闹钟\N{\fs36}because he forgot to set his alarm.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.82,1:54:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当那个工作迟到的人横穿马路的时候\N{\fs36}While that man, late for work, was crossing the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.14,1:54:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy已经彩排结束 正在洗澡\N{\fs36}Daisy had finished rehearsing and was taking a shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.01,1:54:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy洗澡的时候\N{\fs36}And while Daisy was showering,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.43,1:54:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车停在店门口\N{\fs36}the taxi was waiting outside a boutique
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.28,1:54:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等那位女子取包裹\N{\fs36}for the woman to pick up a package
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.14,1:54:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而包裹还没打包好\N{\fs36}which hadn't been wrapped yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.35,1:54:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为打包的女孩\N{\fs36}because the girl who was supposed to wrap it
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.27,1:54:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一晚和她男朋友分手 然后就忘了\N{\fs36}had broken up with her boyfriend the night before and forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.58,1:54:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打包好之后 女子回到出租车上\N{\fs36}When the package was wrapped, the woman, who was back in the cab,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.82,1:54:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被一辆货车挡住去路\N{\fs36}was blocked by a delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.57,1:54:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候 Daisy正在穿衣服\N{\fs36}All the while, Daisy was getting dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.78,1:54:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货车开走了 出租车重新上路\N{\fs36}The delivery truck pulled away, and the taxi was able to move
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.29,1:54:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy最后一个穿好衣服\N{\fs36}while Daisy, the last to be dressed,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.45,1:54:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又等了一会儿她断了鞋带的朋友\N{\fs36}waited for one of her friends who had broken a shoelace.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.46,1:54:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车停下等红绿灯时\N{\fs36}While the taxi was stopped, waiting for a traffic light,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.46,1:54:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy和她朋友从剧院后门出来\N{\fs36}Daisy and her friend came out the back of the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.47,1:54:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有一件事不一样\N{\fs36}And if only one thing had happened differently,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.97,1:54:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果鞋带没有断\N{\fs36}if that shoelace hadn't broken
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.14,1:55:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那货车早一点开走\N{\fs36}or that delivery truck had moved moments earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.77,1:55:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者包裹早已打包好\N{\fs36}or that package had been wrapped and ready
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.98,1:55:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为女孩没跟她男朋友分手\N{\fs36}because the girl hadn't broken up with her boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.82,1:55:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者那个男人定了闹钟 早起5分钟\N{\fs36}or that man had set his alarm and got up five minutes earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.32,1:55:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者司机没有停下来买咖啡\N{\fs36}or that taxi driver hadn't stopped for a cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.61,1:55:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者那个女子记得带外套\N{\fs36}or that woman had remembered
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.52,1:55:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后上了前一辆出租车\N{\fs36}her coat and got into an earlier cab,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.16,1:55:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy和她朋友就能安全穿过马路\N{\fs36}Daisy and her friend would have crossed the street
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.20,1:55:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那出租车也只是擦肩而过\N{\fs36}and the taxi would have driven by.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.47,1:55:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但生活就是这样\N{\fs36}But, life being what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.52,1:55:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一系列生活的交错和意外\N{\fs36}a series of intersecting lives and incidents
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.39,1:55:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能够控制\N{\fs36}out of anyone's control,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.14,1:55:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车没有和她们擦肩而过\N{\fs36}that taxi did not go by,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.85,1:55:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时司机又分了神\N{\fs36}and that driver was momentarily distracted.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.69,1:55:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy\N{\fs36}Daisy!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.02,1:55:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车就撞到了Daisy\N{\fs36}And that taxi hit Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.40,1:55:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy 来人啊\N{\fs36}Daisy! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.07,1:55:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的腿被撞断了\N{\fs36}And her leg was crushed.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.45,1:56:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daisy\N{\fs36}Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.04,1:56:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谁告诉你的  - 你朋友给我写信了\N{\fs36}- Who told you? - Your friend wired me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.55,1:56:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么远来看我 你真是太好了\N{\fs36}Very kind of you to come all this way to see that I was all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.42,1:56:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你 你也会这么做的\N{\fs36}You'd do the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.10,1:56:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs36}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.43,1:56:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你 多完美啊\N{\fs36}Look at you. You're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.92,1:56:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望你没来\N{\fs36}I wish you hadn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.69,1:56:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让你看到我这副样子\N{\fs36}I don't want you to see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.70,1:56:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的腿5处断裂\N{\fs36}Her leg had been broken in five places.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.08,1:56:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果进行长时间治疗 她或许能重新走路\N{\fs36}And with therapy and time, she might walk again.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.75,1:56:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再也不能跳舞了\N{\fs36}But she'd never dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.25,1:56:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要带你回家\N{\fs36}I'm gonna take you home with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.80,1:57:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想照顾你  - 我不回新奥尔良\N{\fs36}- I want to look after you. - I'm not going back to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.68,1:57:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就留在巴黎\N{\fs36}Then I'll stay here in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.47,1:57:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不懂吗 我不想让你帮我\N{\fs36}Don't you understand? I don't want your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.72,1:57:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在是很难过\N{\fs36}I know I'm feeling sorry for myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.48,1:57:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不想跟你在一起\N{\fs36}but I don't want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.94,1:57:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纽约我就告诉你了 你就是不听\N{\fs36}Tried to tell you that in New York. You don't listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.23,1:57:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会改变主意\N{\fs36}You might change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.28,1:57:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都不是小孩儿了 Benjamin\N{\fs36}We are not little children anymore, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.28,1:57:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再掺和我的生活了\N{\fs36}Just stay out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.35,1:57:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太狠心了\N{\fs36}I was awfully cruel.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.69,1:58:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不明白 我只是不想让他看到我那副样子\N{\fs36}He didn't understand. I couldn't have him see me like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.82,1:58:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我并没有马上离开\N{\fs36}"I didn't leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.83,1:58:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在巴黎待了一段时间 暗中照顾她"\N{\fs36}I stayed in Paris for a while to look out for her."
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.71,1:58:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道呢\N{\fs36}I never knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.96,1:58:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 能帮我叫下护士吗\N{\fs36}Oh, darling, could you get the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.72,1:58:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重新学会走路\N{\fs36}I taught myself to walk again.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.90,1:58:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坐了火车去卢尔德\N{\fs36}I took the train to Lourdes.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.82,1:58:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看 很正常 脉搏缓下来了\N{\fs36}Let's take a look. That's normal. Pulse rate is slowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.49,1:58:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后可能会呼吸困难\N{\fs36}She is gonna struggle to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.57,1:58:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 没事\N{\fs36}- Will you be all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.96,1:59:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 他写道 "我回到家"\N{\fs36}All right, he says, "I went back home."
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.64,1:59:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有很多页被撕掉了\N{\fs36}And then there's a lot of pages torn out.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.10,1:59:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我听着房子里的声音" 我读过了\N{\fs36}"I listened to the sound of the house." I read that already.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.72,1:59:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他\N{\fs36}He...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.77,1:59:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把什么洒到纸上了 看不清\N{\fs36}He spilt something on it, so it's hard to read, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.19,1:59:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是关于航海的 你知道是什么吗\N{\fs36}Something about sailing, does that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.69,1:59:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用父亲留在湖边别墅的帆船学会了航行\N{\fs36}I learned to sail an old boat of my father's from the lake house.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.42,1:59:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fs36}I can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.48,1:59:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确很享受有一两位姑娘的陪伴\N{\fs36}I did enjoy the company of a woman or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.68,1:59:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者3位\N{\fs36}Or maybe three.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.78,2:00:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你为什么烦心\N{\fs36}Don't know why you bother,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.56,2:00:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sam 明天还是要去的\N{\fs36}Sam, just gonna be there again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.14,2:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.15,2:00:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1962年春天\N{\fs36}And in the spring of 1962,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.49,2:00:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她回来了\N{\fs36}she came back.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.38,2:01:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你想知道我去哪里了吗  - 不想\N{\fs36}- You want to know where I've been? - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.01,2:01:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也不写信呢\N{\fs36}How come you didn't write or nothing?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.81,2:01:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙就消失了\N{\fs36}Just disappearing like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.02,2:01:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是处理了一下私事\N{\fs36}It was something I needed to do for myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.69,2:01:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛 我也从不觉得你是自私的人\N{\fs36}Yeah, well, I never took you to be the selfish type.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.52,2:01:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此\N{\fs36}I sure hope I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.15,2:01:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看人很准的\N{\fs36}I'm usually not wrong about people.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.32,2:01:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 晚安 妈妈  - 晚安 孩子\N{\fs36}- Good night, Mama. - Good night, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.83,2:01:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们玩得开心\N{\fs36}Y'all have fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.20,2:01:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你都没怎么说话  - 我不想毁了这个气氛\N{\fs36}- You haven't said two words. - I don't want to ruin it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.74,2:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 和我睡吧  - 当然了\N{\fs36}- Sleep with me? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.82,2:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请她跟我出游\N{\fs36}I asked her to come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.49,2:03:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们沿着佛罗里达群岛 一路驶进墨西哥湾\N{\fs36}We sailed into the Gulf along the Florida Keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.95,2:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸26岁那年我没和你在一起\N{\fs36}I am so glad we didn't find one another when I was 26.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.56,2:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 为什么这么说  - 那时我太年轻\N{\fs36}- Why do you say that? - I was so young.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.84,2:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太老了\N{\fs36}And you were so old.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.30,2:03:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓜熟蒂落 水到渠成\N{\fs36}It happened when it was supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.30,2:04:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会珍惜和你在一起的每分每秒\N{\fs36}I will enjoy each and every moment I have with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.60,2:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打赌 我在这能比你坚持得更久\N{\fs36}I bet I can stay out here longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.19,2:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定不行\N{\fs36}I bet you can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.65,2:04:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸上都没有皱纹\N{\fs36}Barely a line or a crease.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.57,2:04:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我每天都会多长几条 不公平\N{\fs36}Every day I have more wrinkles. It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.37,2:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你的皱纹 所有皱纹都爱\N{\fs36}I love your wrinkles. Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.83,2:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越年轻是什么感觉\N{\fs36}What's it like growing younger?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.59,2:04:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好说 我看不到所有变化\N{\fs36}I can't really say. I'm always looking out my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.22,2:04:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我的皮肤下垂变老了 你还爱我吗\N{\fs36}Will you still love me when my skin grows old and saggy?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.28,2:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我的脸上长满青春痘 还尿床 你还爱我吗\N{\fs36}Will you still love me when I have acne? When I wet the bed?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.90,2:04:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我害怕楼梯下的东西时 你还爱我吗\N{\fs36}When I'm afraid of what's under the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.24,2:05:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs36}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.33,2:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\fs36}What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.81,2:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想 为什么没有永恒呢\N{\fs36}Well, I was thinking how nothing lasts.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.96,2:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多遗憾啊\N{\fs36}And what a shame that is.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.72,2:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事情是永垂不朽的\N{\fs36}Some things last.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.64,2:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 晚安 Daisy  - 晚安 Benjamin\N{\fs36}- Good night, Daisy. - Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.29,2:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.62,2:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你什么时候遇见爸爸的  - 在那之后\N{\fs36}- When did you meet Dad? - Some time after that.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.80,2:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他说过Benjamin的事吗\N{\fs36}Did you tell him about this Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.02,2:06:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道得够多了 亲爱的\N{\fs36}He knew enough, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.53,2:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.83,2:06:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Queenie\N{\fs36}Queenie?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.32,2:06:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗\N{\fs36}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.00,2:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Carter太太 我是Benjamin 大家都去哪儿了\N{\fs36}Oh, hi, Mrs. Carter, it's Benjamin. Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.71,2:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin Queenie去世了 我很抱歉\N{\fs36}Oh, Benjamin. Queenie died. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.58,2:07:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节哀顺变吧 她是个了不起的人\N{\fs36}I'm so sorry for your loss. She was a great woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.08,2:07:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们深表哀悼\N{\fs36}Our deepest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.05,2:07:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把她葬在她的挚爱 Weathers先生身边\N{\fs36}We buried her beside her beloved Mr. Weathers.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.16,2:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了过上我们自己的生活\N{\fs36}And so we might have memories of our own,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.65,2:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们卖掉了我父亲的房子\N{\fs36}we sold my father's house on Esplanade.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.69,2:07:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 这房子真是太棒了\N{\fs36}It is a wonderful old place, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.90,2:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里会很幸福的\N{\fs36}I think we are going to be so happy here.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.91,2:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家族历史好久远啊\N{\fs36}Oh, what a long family history you have.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.91,2:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这座房子一样久远\N{\fs36}They come with the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.06,2:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 来吧  - 你一定得看看主卧\N{\fs36}- Come on. - You have to see the master suite.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.92,2:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们买了一套复式公寓\N{\fs36}We bought ourselves a duplex.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.21,2:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特爱那套房子\N{\fs36}I loved that house.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.68,2:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有柴火的味道\N{\fs36}It smelled like firewood.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.76,2:08:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停 继续 亲爱的\N{\fs36}Don't... Don't stop, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.60,2:08:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那是我生命中最快乐的时光"\N{\fs36}"It was one of the happiest times of my life."
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.56,2:08:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连像样的家具都没有\N{\fs36}We didn't have a stick of furniture.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.90,2:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在起居室野餐\N{\fs36}We would have picnics in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.26,2:08:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃饭的时候才吃 只要想 就可以整夜不睡\N{\fs36}We ate when we felt like it. Stayed up all night when we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.53,2:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发誓 不过循规蹈矩的生活\N{\fs36}We vowed never to fall into routine,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.62,2:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不按时睡觉 不按时起床\N{\fs36}to go to bed or wake up at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.58,2:08:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在床垫上生活\N{\fs36}We lived on that mattress.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.58,2:09:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的邻居 Van Dam太太 是个理疗师\N{\fs36}Our neighbor, a Mrs. Van Dam, was a physical therapist.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.42,2:09:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住的地方离公共泳池有四个街区\N{\fs36}We lived four blocks from a public pool.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.54,2:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许 还能多跳几年舞\N{\fs36}You know, you might've got a few more years out of it,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.42,2:10:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你选择的事业太独一无二\N{\fs36}but you chose to do something so special and unique
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.96,2:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有短短几年黄金时期\N{\fs36}that there was only a short window of time you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.51,2:10:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 即使没有发生意外\N{\fs36}So, even if nothing ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.10,2:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是会回到现在的地方\N{\fs36}you'd still be right here where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.31,2:10:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是不喜欢变老\N{\fs36}I just don't like getting old.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.10,2:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在泳池里放了太多漂白粉了\N{\fs36}They put too much chlorine in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.90,2:11:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓 我再也不会自怨自艾了\N{\fs36}I promise you I'll never lose myself to self-pity again.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.12,2:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那时\N{\fs36}And I think right there and then
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.29,2:11:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明白了 没有人能够永远完美\N{\fs36}she realized none of us is perfect forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.25,2:11:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她回归了平静\N{\fs36}She found peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.75,2:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她开了间舞蹈室 教小女孩跳舞\N{\fs36}She opened a studio and taught young girls how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.76,2:11:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足尖点地\N{\fs36}And tendu...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.97,2:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从另一条路回来 点地 点地 点地 好极了\N{\fs36}Come back the other way. And spot, spot, spot. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.73,2:11:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 晚安 Daisy老师  - 晚安\N{\fs36}- Good night, Miss Daisy. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.67,2:12:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很美\N{\fs36}You certainly are beautiful to watch.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.09,2:12:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞最重要的就是身线\N{\fs36}Dancing's all about the line.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.76,2:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的曲线\N{\fs36}The line of your body.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.02,2:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迟早会身材走形 然后再无挽回的余地\N{\fs36}Sooner or later, you lose that line, and you never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.23,2:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是1918年生的 现在49岁了\N{\fs36}I figure, you were born in 1918, 49 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:41.28,2:12:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我43岁\N{\fs36}I'm 43.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.99,2:12:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以算是同龄人了\N{\fs36}We are almost the same age.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.83,2:12:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在人生的中点相遇\N{\fs36}We're meeting in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.67,2:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总算追上彼此了\N{\fs36}We finally caught up with each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.21,2:12:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs36}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.68,2:13:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想记住我们现在的样子\N{\fs36}I want to remember us just as we are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.19,2:13:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs36}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.37,2:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓那护士说漏嘴了 说是男孩\N{\fs36}You know, I swear the nurse slipped and said it was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.02,2:13:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得是女孩\N{\fs36}But I think it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.32,2:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道你很担心  - 我也没藏着\N{\fs36}- I know you're afraid. - I'm not hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.99,2:14:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.45,2:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你最担心什么  - 孩子像我一样出生\N{\fs36}- What's your worst fear? - Baby born like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.12,2:14:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我会更爱他的\N{\fs36}Then I will love it all the more.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.59,2:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越年轻\N{\fs36}Okay. How can I be a father
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.82,2:14:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能当好父亲呢\N{\fs36}when I'm heading in the other direction?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.18,2:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对孩子来说不公平 我也不想变成累赘\N{\fs36}It's not fair to a child. I don't want to be anybody's burden.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.70,2:14:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 到头来我们都会用上尿布\N{\fs36}Sugar, we all end up in diapers.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.93,2:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让一切顺利的\N{\fs36}I am gonna make this work.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.65,2:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要这个孩子 和你一起养\N{\fs36}I want this, and I want it with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.65,2:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的我都会给你\N{\fs36}I want you to have everything you want, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.15,2:14:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是没有想好怎么协调这一切\N{\fs36}I'm just not sure how to reconcile this.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.45,2:14:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会跟盲人说 他不能有孩子吗\N{\fs36}Would you tell a blind man he couldn't have children?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.74,2:14:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs36}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.28,2:14:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是孩子的父亲 能当多久当多久\N{\fs36}You'll be a father for as long as you can.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.83,2:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道会是什么结局 我已经接受了\N{\fs36}I know the consequences. I've accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.71,2:14:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以不惜一切去爱你\N{\fs36}Loving you is worth everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.84,2:15:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上个厕所\N{\fs36}I have to go pee.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.56,2:15:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有史以来横渡英吉利海峡的最年长的妇女\N{\fs36}The oldest woman to ever swim the English Channel
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.90,2:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日抵达加来\N{\fs36}arrived here today in Calais...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.73,2:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不用找了  - 游了34小时\N{\fs36}- Keep it. - ...having made the swim in 34 hours,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.44,2:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,22分14秒\N{\fs36}22 minutes and 14 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.61,2:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现年68岁的Elizabeth Abbott\N{\fs36}The 68-year-old Elizabeth Abbott
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.39,2:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于格林威治时间5点38分抵达\N{\fs36}arrived at 5:38 Greenwich mean time,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.54,2:15:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她精疲力尽 但倍感开心\N{\fs36}exhausted but happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.41,2:15:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abbott女士 能用几句话来总结下您的成功吗\N{\fs36}Miss Abbott, how would you sum up, in words, this achievement?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.04,2:15:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\fs36}I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.04,2:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆有可能\N{\fs36}Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.80,2:15:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了吗  - 好了 谢谢\N{\fs36}- All right? - Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.22,2:15:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可以走了吗  - 非常感谢\N{\fs36}- You ready? - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:48.14,2:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢大家\N{\fs36}Thank you. Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.18,2:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 你们真好\N{\fs36}- Yeah. - You're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.40,2:16:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天 普通的一天里\N{\fs36}In the spring, on a day like any other...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.03,2:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我1小时就回来\N{\fs36}I'll be back in an hour!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.03,2:16:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs36}Honey?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:14.29,2:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去叫救护车\N{\fs36}Go and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.25,2:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快生了\N{\fs36}The baby's coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.75,2:16:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接线员 我要救护车\N{\fs36}Operator, I need an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.88,2:16:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快生了  - 拿破仑路2714号\N{\fs36}- The baby's coming! - 2714 Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.56,2:16:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 保持呼吸\N{\fs36}There you go. Keep breathing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.14,2:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸 用力\N{\fs36}Deep breaths. Push.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.45,2:16:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs36}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:06.26,2:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母女平安 是个健康的女孩儿\N{\fs36}Everyone's fine. She's a perfectly healthy baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.40,2:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs36}Honey?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.64,2:17:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她生下了一个将近4.8斤的女孩\N{\fs36}She gave birth to a five pound, four ounce baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.50,2:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你数了脚趾头吗\N{\fs36}Did you count the toes?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.71,2:17:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好漂亮\N{\fs36}She's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.67,2:17:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们用我母亲的名字给她取名为Caroline"\N{\fs36}"And we named her for my mother, Caroline."
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.68,2:17:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个Benjamin是我爸爸\N{\fs36}This Benjamin was my father?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.35,2:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么告诉我真相的\N{\fs36}And this is how you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.96,2:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fs36}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.91,2:18:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特大飓风所需的条件都已具备\N{\fs36}...because all the ingredients are there for a major storm,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.75,2:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次飓风可高达第5级\N{\fs36}possibly even up to a Category 5.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.05,2:18:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很难受 但不能在这里吸烟\N{\fs36}Hey, I know it's hard. You can't smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:37.01,2:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风登陆点尚不知晓\N{\fs36}Nobody can tell you exactly where it's gonna hit,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.10,2:18:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会查找已有资料\N{\fs36}but we have to go with the guidance that we have,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:41.31,2:18:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整理好信息 并告知你们\N{\fs36}incorporate that information and then pass it along to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.90,2:18:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"正如医生说的 你正常 健康地成长"\N{\fs36}"You grew as the doctor had promised, normal and healthy."
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.42,2:19:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得给她找个真正的父亲\N{\fs36}You're gonna have to find a real father for her.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.67,2:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡说什么\N{\fs36}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.55,2:19:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得有人陪着她慢慢变老\N{\fs36}She's gonna need someone to grow old with.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.93,2:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会学着接受这一切的 她爱你\N{\fs36}She'll learn to accept whatever happens. She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.85,2:19:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 她需要的是父亲 不是玩伴\N{\fs36}Honey, she needs a father, not a playmate.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:26.73,2:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是因为我吗  - 不是\N{\fs36}- Is it me? - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:28.11,2:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是我变老了 你就觉得烦了  - 当然不是\N{\fs36}- Is my age beginning to bother you? - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.19,2:19:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是就这个意思\N{\fs36}Is that what you're telling me?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.48,2:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没法同时养我们两个\N{\fs36}You can't raise the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.87,2:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的1岁生日 我们为你办了场派对\N{\fs36}It was your first birthday. We had a party for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.54,2:19:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间里都是小孩儿\N{\fs36}The house was filled with children.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.46,2:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好啊  - 嘿 兄弟\N{\fs36}- How are you? - Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.51,2:19:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间 他们就该上高中 谈恋爱了\N{\fs36}Before you turn around, they'll be in high school, dating.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.58,2:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卖掉了庞恰特雷恩湖边的避暑别墅\N{\fs36}I sold the summer house on Lake Pontchartrain,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.67,2:20:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖掉了Button纽扣厂\N{\fs36}I sold Button's Buttons,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.51,2:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖掉了我父亲的船 把钱都存进了银行\N{\fs36}I sold my father's sailboat, put it all into a savings account.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.30,2:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你和你妈妈就能过上好日子了\N{\fs36}And so that you and your mother might have a life,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.73,2:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你记得我之前 我离开了你\N{\fs36}I left, before you could ever remember me.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.36,2:21:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我只带走了身上的衣服"\N{\fs36}"I left with just the clothes on my back."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.91,2:21:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再读了\N{\fs36}I don't want to read this now.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.58,2:21:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能直接告诉我他去了哪里吗\N{\fs36}Can you just tell me where he went?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.04,2:21:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs36}I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.55,2:22:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给我的 1970年 我2岁 "生日快乐\N{\fs36}It's for me. 1970. I was two. "Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:11.27,2:22:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我希望我能在临睡前吻你"\N{\fs36}"I wish I could have kissed you good night."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:19.24,2:22:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是给我的\N{\fs36}They're all for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.99,2:22:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5岁 "我希望我能够\N{\fs36}Five. "I wish I could
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.50,2:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你第一天上学的时候领着你去"\N{\fs36}have taken you to your first day of school."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.50,2:22:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6岁 "我希望我可以在你身边 教你弹钢琴"\N{\fs36}Six. "I wish I could have been there to teach you to play piano."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.80,2:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1981年 13岁\N{\fs36}1981,13.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.84,2:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我希望我可以告诉你 别去追那些男生"\N{\fs36}"I wish I could have told you not to chase some boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.47,2:22:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我希望你心碎的时候 有我陪着你"\N{\fs36}"I wish I could have held you when you had a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.64,2:22:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我希望我可以做你的父亲\N{\fs36}"I wish I could have been your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.28,2:22:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么比这更重要"\N{\fs36}Nothing I ever did will replace that."
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.91,2:23:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他去了印度\N{\fs36}I guess he went to India.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.54,2:23:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"有意义的事 再晚做都不迟"\N{\fs36}"For what it's worth, it's never too late,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.54,2:23:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- "不过我应该说 再早做"  - 不过我应该说 再早做\N{\fs36}- "Or, in my case, too early..." - ...or, in my case, too early,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.32,2:23:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你想做的人\N{\fs36}to be whoever you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.17,2:23:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没有时间限制 可以随时开始\N{\fs36}There's no time limit. Start whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.82,2:23:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以改变 也可以一成不变\N{\fs36}You can change or stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.80,2:23:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没有什么规矩\N{\fs36}There are no rules to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.81,2:23:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以活得出彩 也可以一败涂地\N{\fs36}We can make the best or the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.40,2:23:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望你能活出精彩\N{\fs36}And I hope you make the best of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.82,2:23:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能见识到让你惊叹的事\N{\fs36}I hope you see things that startle you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.70,2:23:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能体验你从未体验过的感觉\N{\fs36}I hope you feel things you never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.66,2:23:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能遇见不同想法的人\N{\fs36}I hope you meet people with a different point of view.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:58.33,2:24:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能过着引以为豪的生活\N{\fs36}I hope you live a life you're proud of.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.05,2:24:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你发现你并不觉得自豪 我希望你有勇气\N{\fs36}And if you find that you're not, I hope you have the strength
Dialogue: 0,2:24:09.18,2:24:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 重新开始  - "重新开始"\N{\fs36}- to start all over again. - "...start all over again."
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.93,2:24:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他离开了很长时间\N{\fs36}He had been gone a long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.44,2:24:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周四再见\N{\fs36}I'll see you next Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.53,2:24:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 晚安 Daisy老师  - 晚安 亲爱的\N{\fs36}- Good night, Miss Daisy. - Oh, good night, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.76,2:24:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们下班了\N{\fs36}I'm sorry, we're closing.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.68,2:24:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮你什么吗\N{\fs36}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.81,2:24:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来接孩子的吗\N{\fs36}Are you here to pick somebody up?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.61,2:25:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要回来\N{\fs36}Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:10.07,2:25:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.41,2:25:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.70,2:25:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fs36}You ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.21,2:25:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs36}Mom, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.42,2:25:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是刚听说了一个朋友的噩耗\N{\fs36}I was just hearing a very sad story about a mutual friend
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.09,2:25:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久没见的朋友\N{\fs36}who I hadn't seen for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.05,2:25:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caroline 这是Benjamin\N{\fs36}Caroline, this is Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.88,2:25:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是个婴儿的时候就认识他\N{\fs36}You knew him when you were just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.06,2:25:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs36}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.23,2:25:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs36}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:43.11,2:25:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我以为你准备好了\N{\fs36}Oh, I'm sorry, I thought you were done.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.00,2:25:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这位是我家的世交\N{\fs36}Oh, this is a friend of my family's.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:48.03,2:25:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin Button 这是我丈夫 Robert\N{\fs36}Benjamin Button, this is my husband, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.07,2:25:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好吗  - 幸会\N{\fs36}- How do you do? - A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.63,2:26:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\N{\fs36}Well, it was very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:06.71,2:26:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们在车里等你 亲爱的  - 好的\N{\fs36}- We'll be in the car, darling. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.63,2:26:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs36}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.51,2:26:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去关门\N{\fs36}I'm just locking up.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.01,2:26:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs36}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:20.88,2:26:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真漂亮 跟她妈妈一样\N{\fs36}She's beautiful. Like her mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.11,2:26:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她也跳舞吗  - 跳得不怎么好\N{\fs36}- Does she dance? - Not very well.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.69,2:26:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是遗传我吧\N{\fs36}I guess that'd be from my side of things.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.69,2:26:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个贴心的好姑娘\N{\fs36}She's a dear, sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.86,2:26:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点迷茫 不过 谁12岁的时候不是呢\N{\fs36}She seems a little lost. But then, who isn't at 12?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.41,2:26:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她总是让我想起你\N{\fs36}A lot of her reminds me of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.54,2:26:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫 是鳏夫 呃 曾经是\N{\fs36}My husband, he's a widower, or was... Was a widower.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.88,2:26:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很善良 很阳光 爱冒险\N{\fs36}He's an incredibly kind, just bright, adventurous man.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.97,2:26:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他也是个好父亲  - 真好\N{\fs36}- He's been a terrific father. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.39,2:27:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你又年轻了好多  - 只是外表\N{\fs36}- You are so much younger. - Only on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:07.40,2:27:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs36}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.69,2:27:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法同时养你们两个\N{\fs36}I couldn't have been raising both of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:14.15,2:27:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么坚强\N{\fs36}I'm not that strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:20.12,2:27:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住哪里\N{\fs36}So, where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:24.83,2:27:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算干什么\N{\fs36}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:26.04,2:27:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住在庞恰特雷恩酒店\N{\fs36}I'm staying at the Pontchartrain Hotel on the Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.84,2:27:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该干什么\N{\fs36}I don't know what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.47,2:27:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs36}But...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.14,2:27:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还在等我\N{\fs36}They're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:24.93,2:28:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我记得 那就是他吗\N{\fs36}I remember that. That was him?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.86,2:28:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风改变了方向\N{\fs36}The hurricane has changed directions.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.34,2:28:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后就会登陆\N{\fs36}It's going to make landfall sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.07,2:28:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我是不是该做些什么  - 正在组织\N{\fs36}- Am I supposed to do something? - Arrangements are being made
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.90,2:28:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤离人员 不过还是看你\N{\fs36}to move people, but it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.24,2:28:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我们留下来\N{\fs36}No. No, we're... We're staying.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:39.38,2:28:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况有变我会通知你\N{\fs36}I'll let you know if anything changes.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.87,2:28:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那一晚\N{\fs36}"That night, while I was
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.39,2:28:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坐在那里思考自己为什么回来"\N{\fs36}sitting and wondering why I came back at all,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.33,2:28:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"就有人敲门了"\N{\fs36}"There was a knock at the door."
Dialogue: 0,2:28:54.30,2:28:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs36}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.85,2:29:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs36}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.61,2:29:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不知道我来这里干什么\N{\fs36}I'm sorry, I don't know what I'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.75,2:29:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么会永垂不朽\N{\fs36}Nothing lasts.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.84,2:29:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 这点从未变过\N{\fs36}I have never stopped loving you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.05,2:29:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 Benjamin 我已经老了\N{\fs36}Oh, but, Benjamin, I'm an old woman now.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.40,2:29:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事 你永远不会忘记\N{\fs36}Some things you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.92,2:30:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少有人知道\N{\fs36}...so few people even know
Dialogue: 0,2:30:18.09,2:30:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最初还进过监狱\N{\fs36}that you were ever in jail in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.88,2:30:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你吧 我也觉得不爽\N{\fs36}I'll tell you, I am sick about it, too,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:22.18,2:30:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 就算他们不给你颁"年度人物"这样的大奖\N{\fs36}because, please, if they're not gonna give you an award
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.85,2:30:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们至少能把你的名字\N{\fs36}like "Man of the Year," At least what they could do
Dialogue: 0,2:30:27.01,2:30:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前罪犯档案中除掉\N{\fs36}is stop having you listed as an ex-convict
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.77,2:30:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是觉得 这不公平\N{\fs36}which I think is, again, so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.07,2:30:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.41,2:30:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 Daisy\N{\fs36}Good night, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:53.29,2:30:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和预想的一样 我看着她离开\N{\fs36}And as I knew I would, I watched her go.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:00.26,2:31:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他写的最后一件事了\N{\fs36}That's the last thing he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.72,2:31:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲去世后的一天\N{\fs36}Sometime after your father passed,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.39,2:31:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到一个电话\N{\fs36}there was a call.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:14.31,2:31:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs36}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.56,2:31:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 请讲\N{\fs36}Yes, speaking.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.40,2:31:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我没明白\N{\fs36}I'm sorry, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.71,2:31:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在拐角那个房子停下\N{\fs36}It's the corner house.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.77,2:31:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs36}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.74,2:32:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我是Daisy Fuller  - 我是David Hernandez\N{\fs36}- I'm Daisy Fuller. - I'm David Hernandez,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.12,2:32:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是儿童福利中心奥尔良分局的\N{\fs36}with the Orleans Parish Department of Child Welfare Services.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:10.80,2:32:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在危楼里\N{\fs36}He was living in a condemned building.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:15.12,2:32:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察找到了这个\N{\fs36}The police found this with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.70,2:32:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个日记 里面还很多次提到你的名字\N{\fs36}This address. It's got your name in it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:21.67,2:32:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的健康状况不太乐观 被送去了医院\N{\fs36}He's in very poor health. He was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:24.56,2:32:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都不知道自己是谁 在哪里 他很糊涂\N{\fs36}He doesn't seem to know who or where he is. He's very confused.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:28.55,2:32:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟Hernandez先生说了 Benjamin是我们的一员\N{\fs36}I was telling Mr. Hernandez that Benjamin is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:32.22,2:32:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他需要住的地方 就住这里吧\N{\fs36}If he needs a place to stay, it's all right, he can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.51,2:33:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Benjamin\N{\fs36}Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:10.64,2:33:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弹得真好\N{\fs36}You play beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.93,2:33:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像不喜欢被人碰\N{\fs36}He doesn't seem to like to be touched.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.89,2:33:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他记性时好时坏 认不得人\N{\fs36}He goes in and out of states of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.64,2:33:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说 他们也无能为力\N{\fs36}The doctors say, if they didn't know any better,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.60,2:33:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经有痴呆初期的症状了\N{\fs36}he has the beginnings of dementia.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.61,2:33:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得我吗\N{\fs36}Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:30.53,2:33:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Daisy\N{\fs36}I'm Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.45,2:33:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Benjamin\N{\fs36}I'm Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.92,2:33:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你 Benjamin\N{\fs36}It's nice to meet you, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.90,2:33:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意我和你坐一起吗 我想听你弹\N{\fs36}Would you mind if I sit with you? I would love to hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:55.40,2:33:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识你吗\N{\fs36}Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.92,2:34:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想吃早饭  - 从此之后\N{\fs36}- I want some breakfast. - And every day,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.48,2:34:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都会去看他过得怎么样\N{\fs36}I would stop by to make sure that he was comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.64,2:34:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 我没吃  - 你刚吃完\N{\fs36}- No, I didn't. - You just finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:10.28,2:34:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我不知道你们在搞什么\N{\fs36}Don't think I don't know what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.70,2:34:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都他妈是骗子\N{\fs36}You're all fucking liars!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:15.53,2:34:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不相信他刚吃过早饭了\N{\fs36}He doesn't believe he just had his breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.79,2:34:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来看看\N{\fs36}Now, why don't we see
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.50,2:34:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能找点别的事情做呢\N{\fs36}if we can't find something else for you to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:27.05,2:34:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得 有很多事情我都记不得了\N{\fs36}I have a feeling there's a lot of things I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:30.34,2:34:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如什么呢 宝贝\N{\fs36}Well, like what, sugar?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:33.76,2:34:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 我好像活了很久\N{\fs36}It's like there's this whole life I had,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.97,2:34:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却不记得我的人生\N{\fs36}and I can't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:44.19,2:34:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs36}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.61,2:34:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记事情没什么的\N{\fs36}It's okay to forget things.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:49.32,2:34:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多时候 他不记得自己是谁 在哪\N{\fs36}Many times, he would simply forget who or where he was.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:55.20,2:34:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那儿 屋顶上\N{\fs36}There he is, he's up there on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.99,2:34:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾他不容易\N{\fs36}It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.79,2:35:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Benjamin  - 我可以看到一切\N{\fs36}- Benjamin! - I can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.28,2:35:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能看见大河  - 没错\N{\fs36}- I can see the big river! - That's right,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:03.04,2:35:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都能看到 宝贝\N{\fs36}you can see everything, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:04.98,2:35:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看见妈妈的墓地\N{\fs36}I can see the graveyard where Mama's buried,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:07.04,2:35:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还有很多其他的人  - 快下来\N{\fs36}- and all those other people. - I want you to come down!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:10.38,2:35:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要是会飞呢  - 我就认识个会飞的人\N{\fs36}- What if I could fly? - I knew a man who could fly.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:15.30,2:35:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下来 我就告诉你他的故事\N{\fs36}You come down and I'll tell you all about him.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.68,2:35:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上去接他\N{\fs36}Somebody go up there.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.90,2:35:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搬进去的时候 他5岁\N{\fs36}He was five when I moved in.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:32.94,2:35:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我遇见他时差不多大\N{\fs36}Nearly the same age I was when I had met him.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:43.41,2:35:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这是一只老袋鼠下午5点的样子"\N{\fs36}"This is the picture of Old Man Kangaroo 5 in the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,2:35:50.00,2:35:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他有着粗壮漂亮的后腿"\N{\fs36}"When he had got his beautiful hind legs."
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.72,2:35:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间流逝\N{\fs36}The days passed.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:56.38,2:36:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着他 他不再会走路\N{\fs36}And I watched as he forgot how to walk
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.60,2:36:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 也不会说话  - 我叫什么呀\N{\fs36}- and how to talk. - What's my name?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.58,2:36:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Daisy\N{\fs36}I'm Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:10.98,2:36:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会说"Daisy"吗\N{\fs36}Can you say "Daisy"?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.32,2:36:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2002年 火车站换了新的钟表\N{\fs36}In 2002, they put up a new clock in that train station.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:26.46,2:36:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2003年春天\N{\fs36}And in the spring of 2003,
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.59,2:36:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看着我\N{\fs36}he looked at me
Dialogue: 0,2:36:38.76,2:36:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他认出了我\N{\fs36}and I knew that he knew who I was.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.35,2:36:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 他闭上眼睛 好像睡着了\N{\fs36}And then he closed his eyes as if to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.72,2:37:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 真希望我能认识他  - 现在不就认识了\N{\fs36}- I wish I'd known him. - Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:34.40,2:37:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 我去看看怎么回事\N{\fs36}Mom, I think I should go see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:45.20,2:37:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 Benjamin\N{\fs36}Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:09.64,2:38:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河堤崩塌之后会有山洪\N{\fs36}We're expecting flash flooding after the levee break.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:12.10,2:38:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在9区暴发\N{\fs36}It occurred in the Ninth Ward.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.40,2:38:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定可以坐在河边\N{\fs36}Some people are born to sit by a river.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.74,2:38:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定被闪电击中\N{\fs36}Some get struck by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:25.58,2:38:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定懂音乐\N{\fs36}Some have an ear for music.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:29.29,2:38:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定是艺术家\N{\fs36}Some are artists.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:32.25,2:38:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定是游泳健将\N{\fs36}Some swim.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:35.04,2:38:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定懂纽扣生意\N{\fs36}Some know buttons.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.46,2:38:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定知道莎士比亚\N{\fs36}Some know Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.86,2:38:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定做母亲\N{\fs36}Some are mothers.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.76,2:38:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人生来就注定是舞者\N{\fs36}And some people dance.

